{"type":"message","id":"af11fe0b","parentId":"7bc60c4f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:36:26.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to check the \"skill whitelist\" (技能白名单). In OpenClaw, skills are managed via the `skills` section in the config. Let me look at the relevant part:\n\n```json\n\"skills\": {\n    \"allowBundled\": [\n        \"skill-creator\",\n        \"taskflow\",\n        \"taskflow-inbox-triage\"\n    ],\n    \"load\": {\n        \"extraDirs\": [\n            \"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills\"\n        ],\n        \"watch\": true\n    },\n    \"entries\": {\n        \"update-server\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"gitlab-permission\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"memory-keeper\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"solo-config-field\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"tapd-bug-create\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"tapd-vsmode-story\": {\n            \"enabled\": true\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\nAlso there's a `plugins.allow` list:\n```json\n\"plugins\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n        \"feishu\",\n        \"deepseek\",\n        \"qwen\",\n        \"duckduckgo\"\n    ]\n}\n```\n\nLet me also check what plugin-skills exist in the directory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_adsY8bD8mgIQvabj8phZ6941","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\" -Name","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_M2E9drLq5V5W5NNUev2i3408","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills list 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4622,"output":424,"cacheRead":13312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18358,"cost":{"input":0.0006470800000000001,"output":0.00011872,"cacheRead":0.000372736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001138536}},"stopReaso