{"type":"message","id":"c50ad02e","parentId":"c01a8d32","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:36:34.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive view of the skill configuration. Let me summarize:\n\n**Config Structure:**\n- `skills.allowBundled` — a whitelist of which bundled skills are allowed to load\n- `skills.entries` — individual skill enable/disable settings\n- All skills not in `allowBundled` are blocked by default (that's why many show 🚫 blocked)\n\n**Bundled skills whitelist (`allowBundled`):**\n1. `skill-creator` ✅\n2. `taskflow` ✅\n3. `taskflow-inbox-triage` ✅\n\n**Extra skills (from `plugin-skills/` directory), all enabled:**\n1. `feishu-doc` ✅\n2. `feishu-drive` ✅\n3. `feishu-perm` ✅\n4. `feishu-wiki` ✅\n5. `gitlab-permission` ✅\n6. `memory-keeper` ✅\n7. `solo-config-field` ✅\n8. `tapd-bug-create` ✅\n9. `tapd-vsmode-story` ✅\n10. `update-server` ✅\n\nSo the \"技能白名单\" (skill whitelist) has two parts:\n1. `skills.allowBundled` — only 3 bundled skills are allowed, the rest 59 bundled skills are blocked\n2. All 10 plugin-skills are enabled by virtue of being in `skills.entries` with `enabled: true`\n\nThe user wants to check the skill whitelist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前技能白名单配置如下：\n\n**允许的 Bundled 技能**（`skills.allowBundled`，共 3 个）：\n- ✅ `skill-creator`\n- ✅ `taskflow`\n- ✅ `taskflow-inbox-triage`\n\n其余所有 bundled 技能（共 59 个）均为 🚫 **blocked** 状态 —— 包括 `coding-agent`、`github`、`himalaya` 等。\n\n**Extra 技能**（plugin-skills 目录，共 10 个，全部已启用）：\n- ✅ `feishu-doc` / `feishu-drive` / `feishu-perm` / `feishu-wiki`\n- ✅ `gitlab-permission`\n- ✅ `memory-keeper`\n- ✅ `solo-config-field`\n- ✅ `tapd-bug-create` / `tapd-vsmode-story`\n- ✅ `update-server`\n\n**总结**：白名单目前很精简 —— 只有 3 个 bundled + 10 个 plugin 技能。如果需要把某些 bundled 技能加进白名单（比如 `coding-agent`、`github`），告诉我就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4217,"output":584,"cacheRead":