{"type":"message","id":"a8004231","parentId":"c75b6a64","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:36:54.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the TAPD login references and scripts to understand the cookie setup flow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_BD6QYUYsvq3kcHZl5ViI4609","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\" -Name -Filter *cookie* 2>$null; Get-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\" -Name -Filter *.json 2>$null","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_wAUkTYSAGjtUsNXoYsBa6254","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-bug-create\\references\\tapd-login.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":318,"output":186,"cacheRead":24192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24696,"cost":{"input":0.00004452,"output":0.00005208,"cacheRead":0.0006773759999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007739759999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781491012587,"responseId":"5286f2ac-721b-4eab-8cb0-26013f50be50"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1604c2d3","parentId":"a8004231","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:36:54.651Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_BD6QYUYsvq3kcHZl5ViI4609","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"github_cookies.json\r\ngithub_cookies.json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":222,"aggregated":"github_cookies.json\r\ngithub_cookies.json","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781491014651}}
{"type":"message","id":"97ad7560","parentId":"1604c2d3","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:36:54.652Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_wAUkTYSAGjtUsNXoYsBa6254","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TAPD Login Flow\n\nTAPD uses Tencent Cloud WAF and requires login via:\n\n1. WeChat QR scan (微信扫码) - Headed browser required\n2. SMS verification code (手机验证码)\n3. Email + Password (邮箱密码)\n\n## Cookie Management\n\nLogin cookies are stored in `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`. Storage state is in `workspace/tapd_storage.json`.\n\n## Login via WeChat QR (Recommended)\n\n```mjs\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\nconst page = await (await browser.newContext()).newPage();\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login');\n\n// Click wechat auth\nawait page.click('a[href*=\"wx/auth\"]');\n// QR code appears on screen - scan with phone WeChat\n// Wait for login redirect...\n```\n\n## Login via SMS Code\n\n```mjs\n// Step 1: Send code\n// Navigate, click SMS tab, fill phone, click send\n// Step 2: Enter code\n// Get code from user, fill, submit\n```\n\n## Key Points\n\n- Stealth init script is required for headless mode WAF bypass\n- Headed mode (`headless: false`) always works\n- After login, save cookies with `context.cookies()` and `context.storageState()`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781491014651}}
