{"type":"message","id":"faacf0eb","parentId":"9b09bf94","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:37:03.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so there's a `github_cookies.json` with valid-seeming GitHub cookies. The GitHub cookies look alive (they have `expirationDate` values that are in the future). But the user asked about \"cookie 活性\" — which cookies? Let me think about what's most relevant.\n\nThe user is Yousan(叶枝君) — a developer working on 月圆之夜. The most likely cookies they'd care about are:\n\n1. **TAPD cookies** — `tapd_cookies.json` doesn't exist, so TAPD cookies are **dead/missing**\n2. **GitHub cookies** — `github_cookies.json` exists with cookies that seem valid\n\nLet me verify the GitHub cookies are actually alive by checking expiration. The current time is 2026-06-15 10:36 CST, which is approximately 1781490000 in Unix epoch seconds.\n\nLet me check the key cookie expirations:\n- `__Host-user_session_same_site`: expires 1782443731 → ~2026-06-25 → still valid\n- `dotcom_user`: expires 1812592608 → ~2027-06-06 → still valid\n- `user_session`: expires 1782443731 → ~2026-06-25 → still valid\n- `saved_user_sessions`: expires 1788832608 → ~2026-08-06 → still valid\n- `logged_in`: expires 1812592608 → ~2027-06-06 → still valid\n- `_device_id`: expires 1812766564 → ~2027-06-06 → still valid\n\nAnd session cookies (no expiration) like `_gh_sess`, `cpu_bucket`, `color_mode`, `preferred_color_mode`, `tz`, `last_write_ms` are session-only, which means they'll work as long as the browser session is alive.\n\nSo GitHub cookies are alive and valid.\n\nBut TAPD cookies (`tapd_cookies.json`) don't exist at all. That's a problem.\n\nLet me also quickly verify if the GitHub cookie is actually valid by trying to use it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vwNTuwzlmVB6ZxqUcIK49227","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 快速验证 GitHub cookie 活性\ncurl.exe -s -o NUL -w \"HTTP %{http_code}\\n\" -b \"user_session=S578GzfeZWxUXIfliFc59UinhZ--wJF_Sd-Kv1vg9SFWbEHE\" \"https://github.com/yoshikun\" 2>&1","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_5I8f0W8dJicLnDEVuRVC4872","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否有 tapd 相关 cookie 或 storage 文件\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\" -Name -Filter *tapd* 2>$null\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\" -Name -Filter *storage* 2>$null","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1749,"output":709,"cacheRead":25216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27674,"cost":{"input":0.00024486,"output":0.00019852000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000706048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001149428}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781491017095,"responseId":"fb86681f-98ac-46db-be56-eab4246c139f"}}
