{"type":"message","id":"9b2125b0","parentId":"88a65049","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:37:37.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me also check the latest cron execution states more closely - the last run timestamps indicate when things last tried to run.\n\nLet me organize all this information for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"以下是 OpenClaw 近期的自动化操作日志汇总：\n\n---\n\n## ⏰ Cron 定时任务（3 个）\n\n### 1. TAPD 周以天保活 🟡 异常\n- **时间**：每天 **10:00**（CST）\n- **最近一次**：2026-06-15 10:00 → **⏰ 超时**（120s 耗尽）\n- **连续失败**：**18 次**\n- **原因**：cron job execution timed out — `tapd_keepalive.mjs` 脚本执行超时\n- **备注**：TAPD cookie 文件不存在，脚本实际上没东西可保活\n\n### 2. TAPD 叶枝君保活 🟡 异常\n- **时间**：每天 **10:30**（CST）\n- **最近一次**：2026-06-15 10:30 → **❌ 投递失败**\n- **连续失败**：**18 次**\n- **原因**：脚本试图发送消息到飞书但缺少目标 chatId\n- **备注**：同样 cookie 缺失\n\n### 3. OpenClaw 每日备份 🟡 异常\n- **时间**：每天 **02:00**（CST）\n- **最近一次**：2026-06-14 02:00 → **⏰ 超时**\n- **连续失败**：**3 次**\n- **原因**：cron job execution timed out\n\n---\n\n## 📄 Git 备份历史（最初成功过 3 次）\n```\nb6b3384 add daily backup script and gitignore update\nc2627bb update README with full setup guide and skill details\n651bde5 Initial backup: skills, workspace files, config template, and setup script\n```\n最后一次成功提交是初始设置时，后续全部超时。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 配置审计日志（告警）\n- 5/15 ~ 5/20 期间系统反复检测到 config 文件**size-drop 异常**（34005→10383 bytes，疑似被截断）\n- 写操作被安全机制**自动驳回**（`CONFIG_WRITE_REJECTED`），保留备份\n- 5/20 08:01 最后成功恢复，当前 config 状态正常 ✅\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 最近的一次成功自动化\n- 上次 cron 成功执行只有一条老记录：\n  - **热更流水线**（1778706038821，约一个月前）→ ✅ 成功，已通过飞书通知\n\n---\n\n**需要我帮你修复这些问题吗？**\n1. 重新登录 TAPD 生成 cookie\n2. 修复 cron 超时（比如加长超时时间 / 调整保活脚本）\n3. 修复备份脚本的超时问题"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1521,"output":653,"cacheRead":41216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43390,"cost":{"input":0.00021294,"output":0.00018284,"cacheRead":0.001154048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00