{"type":"message","id":"dad445c9","parentId":"01e134c9","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:39:02.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now it's clear. The cron job is configured to run `tapd_keepalive.mjs` and `daily_backup.ps1` but:\n\n1. **`scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`** — the file doesn't exist at all\n2. **`OpenClaw/daily_backup.ps1`** — let me check that too\n3. **`tapd_cookies.json`** — also doesn't exist\n\nSo the keepalive mechanism is failing because:\n1. The script file itself was never created (or was deleted/never committed)\n2. The TAPD cookie file never existed in the first place\n3. The cron timeout is 120s, but without the script file, it just runs a no-op or errors out\n\nLet me also check if the daily_backup script exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VoBpxOgVnsdQuNZBsCVo0910","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Test-Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\\daily_backup.ps1\"; if (-not $?) { \"not found\" }","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":109,"output":276,"cacheRead":40192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40577,"cost":{"input":0.00001526,"output":0.00007728,"cacheRead":0.001125376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012179159999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781491139892,"responseId":"dabc49dd-85fd-466b-9c98-e487606a6097"}}
