{"type":"message","id":"e3eb85d1","parentId":"e4aefc73","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:39:14.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the backup script exists but the keepalive script doesn't. Let me look more closely at the cron payloads from the jobs.json to understand what exactly was configured.\n\nFrom the earlier output, the cron payload messages were:\n1. TAPD 周以天保活: `运行TAPD保活脚本: node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n2. TAPD 叶枝君保活: `运行TAPD保活脚本: node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\n3. Daily backup: `Run the daily OpenCloud backup. Execute: powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\\daily_backup.ps1\"`\n\nSo the chain of failures is clear. Let me trace through what actually happens:\n\n1. The cron job fires at 10:00\n2. It spawns an isolated sub-agent session\n3. The sub-agent tries to run `node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n4. The script file doesn't exist → Node.js errors out → but the sub-agent might still try to do something\n5. The timeout is 120 seconds, and it times out\n\nBut wait - the jobs.json shows the job has `timeoutSeconds: 120` and the error was \"cron: job execution timed out\" with duration 120759ms, which means it took 120s and hit the timeout.\n\nIf the script doesn't exist, the sub-agent would get an error from `exec` and then it might... actually let me think about what the sub-agent does. The cron payload is:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n  \"message\": \"运行TAPD保活脚本: node C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\scripts\\\\tapd_keepalive.mjs\\n\\n执行完成后检查退出码，如果是1（cookie过期）则用 headed 模式打开 TAPD 登录页，等待主人扫码。退出码0则静默完成即可，不需要通知主人。\",\n  \"toolsAllow\": [\"exec\"],\n  \"timeoutSeconds\": 120,\n  \"lightContext\": true\n}\n```\n\nSo the sub-agent tries to run `node ...tapd_keepalive.mjs`, the file doesn't exist, exec returns an error, and then... it might try to do something else or just hang until timeout.\n\nThe real root issue is simpler than all the chain analysis though. Let me summarize clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"分析了一下，问题链很清楚：\n\n**根本原因：`scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs` 这个文件从头到尾就不存在**\n\n让我梳理整个失效链条：\n\n### 失效链路\n\n1. **脚本文件不存在** ❌\n   - 目录 `scripts/` 根本不存在\n   - 文件 `scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs` 自然也没有\n   - 可以确认——这个保活脚本**从来没被创建过**\n\n2. **Cookie 文件也没有** ❌\n   - `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` 不存在\n   - 即使脚本跑起来了，也没东西可保活\n\n3. **Cron 执行流程**：\n   ```\n   10:00 → 拉起子 agent → exec node tapd_keepalive.mjs → 文件找不到\n   → exec 报错 → 子 agent 卡住（设计是等退出码 0 或 1）→ 120s 超时\n   → 标记为 \"cron: job execution timed out\" → 连续失败 18 次\n   ```\n\n4. **第二个保活任务（10:30）还多了一个问题**：\n   - 脚本跑失败后，子 agent 尝试往飞书发通知\n   - 但 cron 的 `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"` 没有目标 chatId\n   - 投递失败报错 `\"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId>\"`\n\n### 现状汇总\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs` | ❌ 文件不存在 |\n| `tapd_cookies.json` | ❌ 不存在 |\n| 周以天保活 cron（10:00） | ❌ 连续失败 18 次 |\n| 叶枝君保活 cron（10:30） | ❌ 连续失败 18 次 |\n\n**结论：** 这个保活机制从一开始就没真正运作过——脚本没写过，cookie 没存过。需要我重新搭建一套完整的 TAPD 登录 + cookie 保活流程吗？先写保活脚本，然后走一遍 headed 浏览器登录 TAPD 生成 cookie。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14,"output":1082,"cacheRead":40576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41672,"cost":{"input":0.0000019600000000000003,"output":0.00030296,"cacheRead":0.001136128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001441048}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781491143182,"responseId":"09ef6ac2-b779-454a-b35c-45a09ebdf0bf"}}
