{"type":"message","id":"f5a86d35","parentId":"981424fc","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:40:26.248Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_KDwISSeMDfYR5RS2YnId7040","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486)\n⏱️ Uptime: gateway 2d 23h · system 3d 10h\n🧠 Model: deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash · 🔑 api-key (deepseek:default)\n🧮 Tokens: 18k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0030\n🗄️ Cache: 69% hit · 41k cached, 0 new\n📚 Context: 45k/1.0m (4%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f • updated just now\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: high · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.7 (eeef486)\n⏱️ Uptime: gateway 2d 23h · system 3d 10h\n🧠 Model: deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash · 🔑 api-key (deepseek:default)\n🧮 Tokens: 18k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0030\n🗄️ Cache: 69% hit · 41k cached, 0 new\n📚 Context: 45k/1.0m (4%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f • updated just now\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: high · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781491226248}}
