ilure-alert-include-skipped      Count consecutive skipped runs toward\n                                       alerts\n  --failure-alert-mode <mode>          Failure alert delivery mode (announce or\n                                       webhook)\n  --failure-alert-to <dest>            Failure alert destination\n  -h, --help                           Display help for command\n  --keep-after-run                     Keep one-shot job after it succeeds\n                                       (default: false)\n  --light-context                      Enable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --message <text>                     Set agentTurn payload message\n  --model <model>                      Model override for agent jobs\n  --name <name>                        Set name\n  --no-best-effort-deliver             Fail job when delivery fails\n  --no-deliver                         Disable runner fallback delivery\n  --no-failure-alert                   Disable failure alerts for this job\n  --no-light-context                   Disable lightweight bootstrap context for\n                                       agent jobs\n  --session <target>                   Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>                  Set session key for job routing\n  --stagger <duration>                 Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>                Set systemEvent payload\n  --thinking <level>                   Thinking level for agent jobs\n                                       (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --thread-id <id>                     Telegram forum topic thread id\n  --timeout <ms>                       Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>                Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>                          Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram\n                                       chatId, or Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>                      Gateway token (if required)\n  --tools <list>                       Tool allow-list (e.g. exec,read,write or\n                                       exec read write)\n  --tz <iana>                          Timezone for cron expressions (IANA; cron\n                                       default: Gateway host local timezone)\n  --url <url>                          Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to\n                                       gateway.remote.url when configured)\n  --wake <mode>                        Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781491456034}}
