{"type":"message","id":"a6660b0e","parentId":"b20e0195","timestamp":"2026-06-15T02:45:09.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已重新搭建完毕 ✅ 概览如下：\n\n## 新建技能：`tapd-cookie-keepalive`\n\n```\nplugin-skills/tapd-cookie-keepalive/\n├── SKILL.md\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── tapd_login.mjs          # 首次登录用 — headed 浏览器 + 微信扫码\n│   └── tapd_keepalive.mjs      # 保活检查用 — headless 验证 + 自动刷新\n└── references/\n```\n\n**退出码约定：**\n- `0` = 正常，cookie 已刷新 ✅\n- `1` = cookie 过期，需重新登录\n- `2` = cookie 文件不存在\n- `3` = WAF 拦截\n\n## Cron 已更新\n\n| 任务 | 时间 | 脚本路径 | 超时 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| TAPD Cookie 保活 (10:00) | 10:00 CST | `.../tapd_keepalive.mjs` | 60s |\n| TAPD Cookie 保活 (10:30) | 10:30 CST | `.../tapd_keepalive.mjs` | 60s |\n\ncron 子 agent 的流程：执行保活 → 退码 0 静默 / 退码 1 启动 headed 登录等你扫码。\n\n## 还需你操作的一步\n\n**首次需要走一遍登录生成 cookie：**\n\n```bash\nnode C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-cookie-keepalive\\scripts\\tapd_login.mjs\n```\n\n会弹出 headed Chrome 浏览器，微信扫码登录后 cookie 自动保存到 `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`。之后每天的保活 cron 就会自动接上了。\n\n需要我现在帮你跑一遍登录流程吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":43,"output":406,"cacheRead":74240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74689,"cost":{"input":0.000006020000000000001,"output":0.00011368000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00207872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00219842}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781491504795,"responseId":"f905df33-d70a-4990-aaf7-16f3dc51f474"}}
