{"type":"message","id":"b86ba92c","parentId":"02399c8c","timestamp":"2026-06-15T03:04:12.540Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cookies saved. Now let me quickly verify the TAPD cookies are valid by checking the expiration dates.\n\nLet me also check:\n- `tapdsession` expires at 1782097417 → about 2026-06-21\n- `_wt` expires at 1781492913 → wait, that's approximately 174 something... let me calculate\n  - Current time is 2026-06-15 11:03 CST = ~1781492580 (Unix ms / 1000)\n  - `_wt` expires at 1781492913 → that's about 1781492913 - 1781492580 = 333 seconds from now = ~5.5 minutes from now!\n  \nActually let me calculate:\n- 1781492913 in Unix epoch seconds = approximately 2026-06-15 03:08:33 UTC = 2026-06-15 11:08:33 CST\n- Current time is 2026-06-15 11:03 CST\n- So _wt expires in about 5 minutes\n\nAnd `t_i_token` expires at 1781535817 = approximately 2026-06-15 20:23 CST - about 9 hours from now\n\nAnd `tapdsession` expires at 1782097417 = approximately 2026-06-21\n\nSo some cookies are short-lived. The keepalive script will refresh them when it runs. Let me check if it can run right now to verify.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5M0RVxTghXxu2nOdK7ZG7000","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 验证 cookie 过期时间\n$cookies = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_cookies.json\" -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json\n$now = [DateTimeOffset]::UtcNow.ToUnixTimeSeconds()\nWrite-Output \"当前 Unix 时间: $now (当前时间: $(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'))\"\nWrite-Output \"\"\nforeach ($c in $cookies) {\n    if ($c.expirationDate) {\n        $exp = $c.expirationDate\n        $remaining = $exp - $now\n        $dt = [DateTimeOffset]::FromUnixTimeSeconds([long]$exp).LocalDateTime\n        if ($remaining -le 0) {\n            Write-Output \"❌ $($c.name) ($($c.domain)) - 已过期 ($dt)\"\n        } elseif ($remaining -lt 3600) {\n            Write-Output \"⚠️  $($c.name) ($($c.domain)) - 即将过期: 还剩 $([math]::Round($remaining/60)) 分钟 ($dt)\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Output \"✅ $($c.name) ($($c.domain)) - 有效: 还剩 $([math]::Round($remaining/3600,1)) 小时 ($dt)\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Output \"🔵 $($c.name) ($($c.domain)) - session cookie (无过期时间)\"\n    }\n}","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":118,"output":694,"cacheRead":76800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77612,"cost":{"input":0.00001652,"output":0.00019432000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0021504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023612399999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781492645073,"responseId":"351e2e41-5d38-4cbc-a89d-ed3d44832be7"}}
