{"type":"message","id":"3a252d58","parentId":"f9f4d272","timestamp":"2026-06-15T03:06:10.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything looks good. Let me provide a final summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"全部搭建完毕 ✅ 来看最终状态：\n\n---\n\n## 保活机制已就绪\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 技能 `tapd-cookie-keepalive` | ✅ 已创建，已启用 |\n| `scripts/tapd_login.mjs` | ✅ 首次登录用（headed + 微信扫码） |\n| `scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs` | ✅ headless 保活 + 自动刷新 |\n| `playwright` 依赖 | ✅ 已安装（技能本地 node_modules） |\n| `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` | ✅ **13 个 cookies，已通过保活验证** |\n\n### 保活脚本实测结果\n```\n访问 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609 ...\n页面标题: 需求-月圆之夜-TAPD平台  ← 未跳转登录，cookie 有效\nCookies refreshed (13 cookies saved)\nKeepalive successful ✅\n```\n\n### Cron 定时任务\n| 时间 | 任务 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 每日 **10:00** | `tapd_keepalive.mjs` → 退码0静默 / 退码1启动登录 | 60s |\n| 每日 **10:30** | 同上 | 60s |\n\n**流程：** 每天 10:00/10:30 子 agent 执行保活 → 成功则静默 → cookie 过期则启动 headed 浏览器等你扫码 → 再也不会有之前的超时告警了。\n\n如果下次需要手动刷新（以延长有效期），直接找我说「保活一下 TAPD cookie」即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6003,"output":375,"cacheRead":86272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92650,"cost":{"input":0.00084042,"output":0.000105,"cacheRead":0.0024156159999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0033610359999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781492764914,"responseId":"def918fc-b37c-4609-abec-dd02e3e23cc7"}}
