{"type":"message","id":"c4ec015c","parentId":"13cdce98","timestamp":"2026-06-15T04:06:40.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has forwarded a message from someone else (looks like a colleague/PM). The message says:\n\n1. There's an Excel file attached: `yyzy_20260615_付费日志区服字段异常.xlsx`\n2. The message is from someone asking to find a programmer about a payment log issue - the \"server ID\" (区服id) field added to payment logs is incorrect. The example shows that a player's purchase around 4am was for PVP but the server field shows PVE.\n\nThe user forwarded this to me. Let me figure out what they want me to do. The message says \"哈喽有空麻烦找一下程序\" - they want me to find a programmer (程序 = developer) to fix this issue.\n\nThis seems like a bug report / data issue that needs to be filed. I should probably:\n1. Look at the Excel file to understand the issue\n2. Create a TAPD bug ticket about this\n\nLet me first check the Excel file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mkVbUb7ST59XkL6fzeSG2589","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查找飞书传来的附件\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\" -Recurse -Name 2>$null; if (-not $?) { \"no inbound media dir\" }\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\media\" -Recurse -Name 2>$null","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":21269,"output":342,"cacheRead":69504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91115,"cost":{"input":0.00297766,"output":0.00009576,"cacheRead":0.0019461119999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005019532}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781496395321,"responseId":"4bdc61a0-1a2f-4285-8565-7b67bdd4ab79"}}
