{"type":"message","id":"cf91a600","parentId":"74845ab2","timestamp":"2026-06-15T04:06:54.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The xlsx file wasn't delivered to me. The Feishu message mentioned `[File: yyzy_20260615_付费日志区服字段异常.xlsx]` but the actual file wasn't saved to the media directory. This is likely because the Feishu channel only forwards file metadata, not the file content itself.\n\nWhat the user forwarded is a message from a colleague/PM that says:\n1. There's a bug in the payment log system - the \"server ID\" field is wrong\n2. A player's purchase at around 4am was for PVP, but the server field shows PVE\n3. They're asking to \"find a programmer\" to fix this\n\nThe user Yousan(叶枝君) forwarded this to me - they want me to help. Since Yousan is a developer (the git profile says yezhijun@ztgame.com), the \"programmer\" referred to might be themselves or another developer.\n\nLooking at the context: Yousan(叶枝君) is the person I'm talking to. The forwarded message says \"有空麻烦找一下程序\" - this is someone asking Yousan to find a programmer. But Yousan forwarded it to me - probably wanting me to file this as a bug in TAPD.\n\nLet me:\n1. Read the Excel file if available, or work with the info provided\n2. File a TAPD bug ticket\n\nSince I can't get the xlsx file, I should ask the user if they want me to file a TAPD bug based on the information available, or if they can provide more details.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. Yousan is the developer (程序/程序员) who works on the payment log system. The forwarded message is from a PM/QA saying the \"server ID\" field in payment logs is still wrong. Yousan forwarded this to me - they probably want me to:\n1. Look into what the issue is\n2. File it as a bug ticket in TAPD\n\nBut I don't have the xlsx file contents. Let me let Yousan know the file wasn't saved and ask what they'd like to do.\n\nActually wait - Yousan is the one who forwarded this to me, and Yousan IS the programmer (叶枝君). So this is a bug report about something Yousan or their team worked on. Let me just ask if they want me to create a TAPD bug ticket with the info we have.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"飞书的附件（`yyzy_20260615_付费日志区服字段异常.xlsx`）没有自动保存到本地，我没法直接读内容。\n\n不过我整理了已有的信息，需要我帮你在这个基础上在 TAPD 提一个 Bug 吗？\n\n**已知信息：**\n- **问题：** 支付日志的「区服 ID」字段不准确\n- **例子：** 某个账号 4 点左右的购买是 PVP 充值，但给的区服是 PVE\n- **附件：** `yyzy_20260615_付费日志区服字段异常.xlsx`（你有这个文件的话可以发给我）\n\n你能把这个 xlsx 发给我，或者告诉我更多细节（比如要分配给谁、优先级、Bug 标题），我直接提单？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":123,"output":689,"cacheRead":93184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93996,"cost":{"input":0.00001722,"output":0.00019292000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002609152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002819292}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781496404610,"responseId":"608c5c90-29cb-49ed-a666-71fe2a2c60ab"}}
