{"type":"message","id":"db69e251","parentId":"1ecde513","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:17:36.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! There's `.cursor/plans/` with a `.plan.md` file. This is how Cursor's agent tracks tasks. Let me look at it and also explore the `e-Solo-nightoffullmoon` project (this looks like the 月圆之夜 project - Solo of Night Full Moon).\n\nLet me check the Cursor skills, especially the `loop` skill which sounds promising for what we want.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KW94lSBlLfnfuoPWkHzN8513","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Write-Output \"=== plan file ===\"\nGet-Content \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\plans\\围棋拍照棋谱小程序_71783b8c.plan.md\" -Head 20\n\nWrite-Output \"=== project e-Solo-nightoffullmoon ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\projects\\e-Solo-nightoffullmoon\" -Name | Select-Object -First 20\n\nWrite-Output \"=== cursor skills - loop ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\skills-cursor\\loop\" -Recurse -Name\n\nWrite-Output \"=== cursor skills - automate ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\skills-cursor\\automate\" -Recurse -Name","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":315,"output":318,"cacheRead":116096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116729,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.00008904,"cacheRead":0.003250688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0033838279999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504252885,"responseId":"0634fd5f-a83c-4742-8bd0-275f59222288"}}
