{"type":"message","id":"dce6d795","parentId":"c14b934a","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:19:22.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `cursor agent` seems to start and exit without producing output when piped input from PowerShell. It's designed for interactive use.\n\nLet me take a completely different approach. Instead of trying to make cursor agent work via pipe, I'll:\n\n1. Create an OpenClaw skill `cursor-bridge`\n2. The skill will include a bridge script that Cursor's MCP can call\n3. When I want to send a task to Cursor, I'll write it to a file that the bridge manages\n\nBut actually, maybe the simplest approach that WILL work is:\n\n**Let me check if `cursor --chat` opens a chat window with a message** - maybe there's a way.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. I've been overcomplicating this. Let me check if there's a simpler path:\n\n1. `cursor -g <file>` - opens a file at a specific position\n2. `cursor --chat` - opens standalone chat\n\nWhat if I combine these? Like, write a task to a TODO file and open it in Cursor?\n\nOr even simpler - what if I just use the `exec` tool to run `cursor` commands directly? For example:\n- `cursor -g \"D:\\Solo\\path\\to\\file.ts:42\"` - opens a specific file at a line\n- This is useful for code review / navigation tasks\n\nBut for actual task execution, I need `cursor agent`.\n\nLet me try a key approach I haven't tried yet: **starting cursor agent in a new terminal window**.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VdNrJ69ETOy7ALs3MN2W2930","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try starting cursor agent in a new window with a specific task\n# This uses start /b to run in background\n$task = \"请在 D:\\Solo 项目中，找到支付日志相关的代码文件\"\nStart-Process -WindowStyle Hidden -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\cursor\\resources\\app\\bin\\cursor.cmd\" -ArgumentList \"agent\" -NoNewWindow -RedirectStandardInput \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_in.txt\" -RedirectStandardOutput \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_out.txt\" -RedirectStandardError \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_err.txt\"\n\n# Write task to the input file\n$task | Out-File -FilePath \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_in.txt\" -Encoding utf8\n\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 5\n\n# Check output\nWrite-Output \"=== Output ===\"\nGet-Content \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_out.txt\" -Tail 20 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nWrite-Output \"=== Error ===\"\nGet-Content \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_err.txt\" -Tail 10 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":187,"output":614,"cacheRead":137600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138401,"cost":{"input":0.000026180000000000003,"output":0.00017192000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0038528,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0040509}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504354020,"responseId":"196bba1c-4a1b-4cd6-aa10-445e4c7d93fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd0f8b2d","parentId":"dce6d795","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:19:27.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_VdNrJ69ETOy7ALs3MN2W2930","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Start-Process : 不能同时指定“-NoNewWindow”和“-WindowStyle”参数。\r\n所在位置 行:4 字符: 1\r\n+ Start-Process -WindowStyle Hidden -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppD ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]，InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidOperationException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StartProcessCommand\r\n \r\n=== Output ===\r\n=== Error ===\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":5250,"aggregated":"Start-Process : 不能同时指定“-NoNewWindow”和“-WindowStyle”参数。\r\n所在位置 行:4 字符: 1\r\n+ Start-Process -WindowStyle Hidden -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppD ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]，InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidOperationException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StartProcessCommand\r\n \r\n=== Output ===\r\n=== Error ===\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781504367718}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea2bf783","parentId":"cd0f8b2d","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:19:38.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, let me step back and give the user a realistic assessment. The `cursor agent` command is designed for interactive terminal use and doesn't easily accept piped input from external processes.\n\nHere's what I've learned:\n\n1. **Cursor CLI exists** at `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\cursor\\resources\\app\\bin\\cursor.cmd`\n2. **`cursor agent`** starts an interactive agent that reads from user input at the terminal\n3. **No `cursor exec \"task\"`** command exists to send one-shot tasks\n4. **`cursor --chat`** opens a standalone chat GUI window\n5. **`cursor -g file:line`** navigates to a file position\n6. **MCP `cursor-app-control`** exists for controlling Cursor from within Cursor\n\nThe realistic approaches I can offer:\n\n**Approach A: Node.js bridge script (most promising)**\nI can write a Node.js script that:\n- Uses `node-pty` (or `windows-pty` equivalent) to spawn `cursor agent` in a pseudo-terminal\n- Creates a local HTTP server for receiving tasks\n- I call the HTTP endpoint when you send a message on phone\n- The script pipes the task to cursor agent via the PTY\n\nThis would need `node-pty` installed.\n\n**Approach B: File-based task queue**\n- I write task files to a project directory\n- Cursor's agent watches for new task files (the `loop` skill can be used)\n- When a task file appears, Cursor agent picks it up and executes it\n\n**Approach C: Cursor Automation (simplest)**\n- Create a Cursor Automation with a webhook trigger\n- When I receive a message from you, I call the webhook\n- Cursor Automation executes the task\n\nLet me present these options to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"试了几种方式，结论如下：\n\n## `cursor agent` 的限制\n\n`cursor agent` 是**交互式终端程序**，不接受 stdin pipe 传指令，也没 `cursor exec \"xxx\"` 这种一键执行命令。直接桥接不太行。\n\n## 可行的方案\n\n### 方案 A：Node.js PTY 桥接脚本 ⭐ 推荐\n我写一个 Node.js 脚本，用 `node-pty` 创建一个伪终端来启动 `cursor agent`，然后我通过 HTTP/WebSocket 发指令给它，它在伪终端里模拟键盘输入。\n\n```\n手机飞书 → 我 → HTTP → bridge 脚本 → PTY → cursor agent → 执行任务\n```\n\n需要安装 `node-pty`（Windows 上有些门槛）。\n\n### 方案 B：文件队列 + Cursor loop\n- 我在项目目录写 `.cursor/tasks/pending.md`\n- 你在 Cursor 里用 `/loop 30s 检查并执行 .cursor/tasks/pending.md 里的任务`\n- Cursor 的 loop 技能会轮询，发现新任务就自动执行\n\n```\n手机飞书 → 我 → 写 task 文件 → Cursor loop 检测到 → 自动执行\n```\n\n**优点：** 不需要任何额外依赖，纯粹靠 Cursor 已有能力\n**缺点：** 需要你在 Cursor 里手动启动一次 loop，之后就一直后台跑\n\n### 方案 C：`cursor -g` 导航 + 手动触发\n我收到消息后，把相关代码文件用 `cursor -g \"文件路径:行号\"` 打开，你在 Cursor 里按 `Ctrl+I` 触发 agent 执行。\n\n---\n\n你倾向哪个方案？如果选 **B** 我现在就能搭起来，你先试试效果。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":180,"output":781,"cacheRead":138368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139329,"cost":{"input":0.000025200000000000003,"output":0.00021868000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003874304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0041181839999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781504367721,"responseId":"966129fe-0312-49c7-8d36-3b55373a04c7"}}
