{"type":"message","id":"a9767dab","parentId":"f878c840","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:22:17.185Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**`node-pty` works!** The PTY successfully emulated a terminal, ran `cmd.exe`, received commands, and returned output properly. Now I can build the bridge.\n\nNow let me create the full bridge script. Here's the architecture:\n\n1. **Bridge Server** (`bridge_server.mjs`):\n   - Starts `cursor agent` in a `node-pty` pseudo-terminal\n   - Runs an HTTP server on a local port (e.g., 18790)\n   - Listens for POST requests with a task instruction\n   - Sends the instruction to cursor agent via PTY\n   - Captures the output and returns it as the response\n\n2. **The flow**:\n   - User sends message on phone (Feishu) → OpenClaw\n   - OpenClaw receives the message\n   - OpenClaw POSTs the task to bridge_server at `http://localhost:18790/execute`\n   - Bridge server sends it to cursor agent via PTY\n   - Bridge server streams back cursor agent's output\n   - OpenClaw returns the result to the user\n\nLet me create this as a skill.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CaMsBdXEh16Sn5jGc3vV2138","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"测试 node-pty 可用 ✅","status":"completed"},{"step":"创建 cursor-bridge 技能骨架","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"编写 bridge_server.mjs（HTTP + PTY 桥接）","status":"pending"},{"step":"编写 SKILL.md","status":"pending"},{"step":"启动桥接服务并验证","status":"pending"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":408,"output":364,"cacheRead":135936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136708,"cost":{"input":0.00005712,"output":0.00010192000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0038062079999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003965247999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504532168,"responseId":"8e84d3f5-d533-431a-9e19-76aac1f171bd"}}
