{"type":"message","id":"7a40c0e6","parentId":"74f7068c","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:23:05.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me test the bridge server. But first, I realize the script has issues with ESM (it uses `import` statements but the script is `.mjs`). Let me check:\n\nThe script is `bridge_server.mjs` which is good for ESM. But it uses `import http from 'http'` etc. which is ESM syntax. And it imports `fileURLToPath` from 'url'. These are all fine.\n\nHowever, the `spawn` from 'child_process' is fine too.\n\nLet me test starting it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aJu5Di1L3m4bJxJ7AgV80538","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 启动桥接服务测试（后台运行）\n$env:PROJECT_DIR = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n$ps = Start-Process -NoNewWindow -PassThru -FilePath \"node\" -ArgumentList @(\n  \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\scripts\\bridge_server.mjs\",\n  \"--port=18790\",\n  \"--project=C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n)\nWrite-Output \"PID: $($ps.Id)\"\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 3\n\n# 检查是否在运行\ncurl.exe -s http://127.0.0.1:18790/status 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":223,"output":338,"cacheRead":141056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141617,"cost":{"input":0.00003122,"output":0.00009464,"cacheRead":0.003949568,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004075428}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504580649,"responseId":"d29ed6ca-5aa2-4296-b778-28dc1914938d"}}
