{"type":"message","id":"588e889b","parentId":"548e0e03","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:23:47.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me test this with a proper PTY. I need to run the bridge server in the background, wait for it to start, then test the API.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vzDaI2y0FYq7h9Z5r5iz8170","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Start the bridge server in background\n$logFile = \"$env:TEMP\\cursor_bridge.log\"\n$ps = Start-Process -NoNewWindow -PassThru -FilePath \"node\" -ArgumentList @(\n  \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\scripts\\bridge_server.mjs\",\n  \"--port=18790\"\n) -RedirectStandardOutput $logFile -RedirectStandardError $logFile\n\nWrite-Output \"Started bridge PID: $($ps.Id)\"\nWrite-Output \"Log: $logFile\"\n\n# Wait for startup\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 5\n\n# Check log\nWrite-Output \"=== Log ===\"\nGet-Content $logFile\n\n# Check status\nWrite-Output \"=== Status ===\"\ntry { curl.exe -s --connect-timeout 5 http://127.0.0.1:18790/status 2>&1 } catch { Write-Output \"Not ready yet\" }","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":47,"output":302,"cacheRead":145024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145373,"cost":{"input":0.0000065800000000000005,"output":0.00008456,"cacheRead":0.0040606719999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0041518119999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504624072,"responseId":"92b5c482-e0d7-4052-9aa7-7a29b12309b8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a37fc783","parentId":"588e889b","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:23:53.528Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_vzDaI2y0FYq7h9Z5r5iz8170","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Start-Process : 无法运行此命令，因为“RedirectStandardOutput”和“RedirectStandardError”相同。请指定不同的输入，然后再次运\r\n行此命令。\r\n所在位置 行:3 字符: 7\r\n+ $ps = Start-Process -NoNewWindow -PassThru -FilePath \"node\" -Argument ...\r\n+       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]，InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidOperationException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StartProcessCommand\r\n \r\nStarted bridge PID: \r\nLog: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\cursor_bridge.log\r\n=== Log ===\r\nGet-Content : 找不到路径“C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\cursor_bridge.log”，因为该路径不存在。\r\n所在位置 行:16 字符: 1\r\n+ Get-Content $logFile\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ObjectNotFound: (C:\\Users\\yyzypu...rsor_bridge.log:String) [Get-Content], ItemNotFoundEx \r\n   ception\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : PathNotFound,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.GetContentCommand\r\n \r\n=== Status ===\r\n{\"running\":false,\"ready\":false,\"queue\":0,\"processing\":false,\"projectDir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"cursorBinary\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\cursor\\\\resources\\\\app\\\\bin\\\\cursor.cmd\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5787,"aggregated":"Start-Process : 无法运行此命令，因为“RedirectStandardOutput”和“RedirectStandardError”相同。请指定不同的输入，然后再次运\r\n行此命令。\r\n所在位置 行:3 字符: 7\r\n+ $ps = Start-Process -NoNewWindow -PassThru -FilePath \"node\" -Argument ...\r\n+       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]，InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorI