{"type":"message","id":"66ebabac","parentId":"a37fc783","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:23:58.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The server is running but the cursor agent didn't start. The status shows `running: false` which means `ptyProcess` is null after starting. The agent might have failed to start or the cursor agent might have an issue with the PTY.\n\nLet me check - maybe the `cursor agent` command doesn't work well in a PTY either because it detects it's in a non-GUI context. Let me check the console output.\n\nActually, the status returned successfully from the HTTP server, which means the server IS running. But `running: false` means ptyProcess was created but then exited, or the PTY creation failed.\n\nLet me try running the bridge server directly in this session to see the output.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c9RCCGl25TE8FhTb2O6q3999","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Kill previous bridge\nGet-Process -Name \"node\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.CommandLine -match \"bridge_server\" } | Stop-Process -Force 2>$null\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 1\n\n# 启动桥接，让我们看到完整输出\nnode \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\scripts\\bridge_server.mjs\" --port=18791 2>&1 &\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 8\n\n# 检查状态\ncurl.exe -s http://127.0.0.1:18791/status 2>&1","pty":true,"timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":482,"output":362,"cacheRead":145280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146124,"cost":{"input":0.00006748000000000001,"output":0.00010136,"cacheRead":0.00406784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00423668}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781504633532,"responseId":"55163895-59dd-472c-8c5d-be77df64dba2"}}
