{"type":"message","id":"a9b7805f","parentId":"8e20d97c","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:25:51.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_tDuTVR4Ra4AX4F4tBkft3092","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pending Task\r\n\r\n- **ID:** mqetxhag\r\n- **Time:** 2026/6/15 14:25:48\r\n- **From:** 鍙舵灊鍚?(via Feishu)\r\n\r\n## Instruction\r\n\r\n鎵惧埌鏀粯鏃ュ織鐩稿叧浠ｇ爜锛屾鏌ュ尯鏈岻D瀛楁閫昏緫\r\n{\r\n  \"taskId\": \"mqetxhag\",\r\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-15T06:25:48.232Z\",\r\n  \"instruction\": \"鎵惧埌鏀粯鏃ュ織鐩稿叧浠ｇ爜锛屾鏌ュ尯鏈岻D瀛楁閫昏緫\",\r\n  \"status\": \"pending\",\r\n  \"created\": true\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":181,"aggregated":"# Pending Task\r\n\r\n- **ID:** mqetxhag\r\n- **Time:** 2026/6/15 14:25:48\r\n- **From:** 鍙舵灊鍚?(via Feishu)\r\n\r\n## Instruction\r\n\r\n鎵惧埌鏀粯鏃ュ織鐩稿叧浠ｇ爜锛屾鏌ュ尯鏈岻D瀛楁閫昏緫\r\n{\r\n  \"taskId\": \"mqetxhag\",\r\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-15T06:25:48.232Z\",\r\n  \"instruction\": \"鎵惧埌鏀粯鏃ュ織鐩稿叧浠ｇ爜锛屾鏌ュ尯鏈岻D瀛楁閫昏緫\",\r\n  \"status\": \"pending\",\r\n  \"created\": true\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781504751165}}
{"type":"message","id":"a68b6671","parentId":"a9b7805f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:25:57.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see some encoding issues with Chinese characters - the content was written with UTF-8 but it appears garbled in the output. Let me fix this by ensuring proper encoding. But actually, this is just a display issue in the PowerShell output. The file content itself is fine.\n\nNow let me also create a cursor skill that the user can use to set up the loop watcher. Let me write it to the project's cursor skills.\n\nLet me now:\n1. Clean up the test artifacts\n2. Write the cursor skill file for the project\n3. Test the full flow\n4. Clean up background processes","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QacswaTXeNN5MVAYba2e7312","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Cursor Bridge - Task Watcher\n\nWatches `.cursor/tasks/pending.md` for new tasks and executes them.\nTasks are submitted from OpenClaw (via Feishu/phone).\n\n## Quick Start\n\n在 Cursor Agent 中运行一次：\n\n```\n/loop 30s 读取 D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\tasks\\pending.md 和 D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\tasks\\status.json，如果有新的 pending 任务（检查 status.json 里的 status 是否为 \"pending\"），则：\n1. 执行 pending.md 里的 Instruction 内容\n2. 执行完成后，将 status.json 的 status 改为 \"completed\"\n3. 将 pending.md 重命名为 done_<taskId>.md\n```\n\nLoop 启动后，Cursor Agent 每 30 秒检查一次。有新任务时自动执行。\n\n## Manual Execution\n\n你也可以手动执行：\n\n```\n读取 D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\tasks\\pending.md 的内容并执行里面的任务\n```\n\n## Task File Format\n\n```markdown\n# Pending Task\n\n- **ID:** <taskId>\n- **Time:** <timestamp>\n- **From:** 叶枝君 (via Feishu)\n\n## Instruction\n\n<具体的任务指令>\n```\n","path":"D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\skills-cursor\\cursor-bridge\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":334,"output":456,"cacheRead":163840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164630,"cost":{"input":0.000046760000000000006,"output":0.00012768,"cacheRead":0.00458751999