{"type":"message","id":"35a037b7","parentId":"089dd379","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:31:56.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the window handles! I see:\n- `267130 ● agent - Cursor` - This is the cursor agent window!\n- `2364312 C:\\Windows\\system32\\cmd.exe` - The cmd window we opened\n- `854718 Cursor Agents` - Another cursor agent window\n- `788774 安装 - Cursor (User)` - Cursor settings\n\nSo cursor agent IS running in a window. Now I need to send keystrokes to that window to interact with it.\n\nLet me use Windows API to find the agent window and send keystrokes to it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vBmfuGG2D9hot2dPLEq11996","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 找到 cursor agent 窗口并发送指令\nAdd-Type -AssemblyName System.Windows.Forms\n\n# 查找 agent 窗口\n$hwnd = 267130  # from previous output, \"● agent - Cursor\"\n\n# 激活窗口\n$sig = @'\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern bool SetForegroundWindow(IntPtr hWnd);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern bool ShowWindow(IntPtr hWnd, int nCmdShow);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern IntPtr GetForegroundWindow();\n'@\n$winApi = Add-Type -MemberDefinition $sig -Name \"WinAPI\" -Namespace Win32 -PassThru\n\n# Bring window to foreground\n$winApi::ShowWindow($hwnd, 5)  # SW_SHOW\n$winApi::SetForegroundWindow($hwnd)\nStart-Sleep -Milliseconds 500\n\nWrite-Output \"Foreground window HWND: $($winApi::GetForegroundWindow())\"\n\n# Send test keystroke\n[System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"echo hello from openclaw bridge{ENTER}\")\nStart-Sleep -Milliseconds 500\n[System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"list files in current directory{ENTER}\")\n\nWrite-Output \"Keystrokes sent to cursor agent window\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1905,"output":480,"cacheRead":168704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":171089,"cost":{"input":0.00026670000000000003,"output":0.00013440000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004723712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005124811999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781505111457,"responseId":"0f666245-f8e1-4970-aab9-0e6c8be5e460"}}
{"type":"message","id":"42d8f284","parentId":"35a037b7","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:31:58.631Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_vBmfuGG2D9hot2dPLEq11996","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"True\r\nFalse\r\nForeground window HWND: 0\r\n使用“1”个参数调用“SendWait”时发生异常:“拒绝访问。”\r\n所在位置 行:23 字符: 1\r\n+ [System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"echo hello from openclaw b ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], MethodInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : Win32Exception\r\n \r\n使用“1”个参数调用“SendWait”时发生异常:“拒绝访问。”\r\nKeystrokes sent to cursor agent window\r\n所在位置 行:25 字符: 1\r\n+ [System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"list files in current dire ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], MethodInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : Win32Exception"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1647,"aggregated":"True\r\nFalse\r\nForeground window HWND: 0\r\n使用“1”个参数调用“SendWait”时发生异常:“拒绝访问。”\r\n所在位置 行:23 字符: 1\r\n+ [System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"echo hello from openclaw b ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], MethodInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : Win32Exception\r\n \r\n使用“1”个参数调用“SendWait”时发生异常:“拒绝访问。”\r\nKeystrokes sent to cursor agent window\r\n所在位置 行:25 字符: 1\r\n+ [System.Windows.Forms.SendKeys]::SendWait(\"list files in current dire ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], MethodInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : Win32Exception","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781505118631}}
{"type":"message","id":"602c72b7","parentId":"42d8f284","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:32:06.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\"Access denied\" on SendKeys - this is a security restriction. SendKeys doesn't work when running as a background service/process without a desktop session. I'm running inside the OpenClaw gateway which might be running as a service or in a non-interactive session.\n\nLet me try using `user32.dll`'s `SendMessage` or `PostMessage` to send keystrokes directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HmdzTN4zbmrc1G9Y1xw27518","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用 user32 SendMessage 发送按键\n$sig = @'\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern int SendMessage(IntPtr hWnd, int Msg, int wParam, int lParam);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern bool PostMessage(IntPtr hWnd, int Msg, int wParam, int lParam);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern IntPtr FindWindowEx(IntPtr parent, IntPtr child, string className, string windowName);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern int GetWindowTextLength(IntPtr hWnd);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)] public static extern int GetWindowText(IntPtr hWnd, System.Text.StringBuilder text, int count);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern uint GetWindowThreadProcessId(IntPtr hWnd, out uint lpdwProcessId);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")] public static extern IntPtr SendMessage(IntPtr hWnd, int Msg, int wParam, System.Text.StringBuilder lParam);\n'@\n$user32 = Add-Type -MemberDefinition $sig -Name \"User32\" -Namespace Win32 -PassThru\n\n# WM constants\n$WM_GETTEXT = 0x000D\n$WM_GETTEXTLENGTH = 0x000E\n$WM_SETTEXT = 0x000C\n$WM_CHAR = 0x0102\n$WM_KEYDOWN = 0x0100\n$WM_KEYUP = 0x0101\n\n$hwnd = 267130  # \"● agent - Cursor\"\n\n# Get window text\n$len = $user32::GetWindowTextLength($hwnd)\n$sb = New-Object System.Text.StringBuilder ($len + 1)\n$user32::SendMessage($hwnd, $WM_GETTEXT, $len + 1, $sb)\nWrite-Output \"Window title: $sb\"\n\n# Try to find child windows (edit control, etc.)\n$edit = $user32::FindWindowEx($hwnd, [IntPtr]::Zero, \"Edit\", $null)\nif ($edit -ne [IntPtr]::Zero) {\n    Write-Output \"Found Edit control: $edit\"\n    # Send text\n    $text = \"echo test from openclaw`n\"\n    foreach ($c in $text.ToCharArray()) {\n        $user32::PostMessage($edit, $WM_CHAR, [int]$c, 0)\n    }\n    Write-Output \"Sent chars to edit\"\n} else {\n    Write-Output \"No Edit child found\"\n    # Try other window classes\n    $classes = @(\"RICHEDIT\", \"RICHEDIT50W\", \"Scintilla\", \"TextBox\", \"Text\", \"ConsoleWindow\", \"MozillaWindowClass\")\n    foreach ($cls in $classes) {\n        $child = $user32::FindWindowEx($hwnd, [IntPtr]::Zero, $cls, $null)\n        if ($child -ne [IntPtr]::Zero) {\n            Write-Output \"Found $cls: $child\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# Get PID for the window\n$pid = 0\n$user32::GetWindowThreadProcessId($hwnd, [ref]$pid)\nWrite-Output \"Process ID: $pid\"\nGet-Process -Id $pid -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, ProcessName, StartTime","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":313,"output":907,"cacheRead":171008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172228,"cost":{"input":0.000043820000000000004,"output":0.00025396,"cacheRead":0.004788224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005086004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781505118634,"responseId":"073928e5-f253-4b0b-bf7b-04c280dc7117"}}
