{"type":"message","id":"ede41366","parentId":"d46933f6","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:33:46.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The CLI is minified code. It's impractical to reverse engineer.\n\nLet me step back and give the user a clear, honest assessment. I've spent a lot of effort trying to bridge OpenClaw and Cursor in real-time. Here's the honest situation:\n\n1. **`cursor agent` headless**: Does NOT work. It requires a real interactive terminal window.\n2. **Windows UI automation**: Possible but very fragile, and `SendKeys` is blocked (access denied). `PostMessage` works but window handles expire.\n3. **`--add-mcp`**: This IS a viable approach. Let me explain how it works.\n\nThe MCP approach:\n- I run a local MCP server\n- Register it with Cursor using `cursor --add-mcp`\n- The MCP server provides a tool like `execute_task` that accepts instructions\n- When the user wants to use it, they talk to Cursor agent and say \"ask openclaw to do X\"\n- Cursor's agent calls my MCP tool, which executes the task\n\nThis gives \"real-time conversation\" in the sense that:\n- User sends message from phone → I receive it\n- I can prepare instructions or files\n- User opens Cursor agent and says \"continue the task from openclaw\"\n- Cursor agent calls my MCP tool to get context and instructions\n- The agent executes and the user sees the result in the agent conversation\n\nFor complete push-based communication without user involvement, I would need to:\n- Create a Cursor extension that opens a WebSocket to my bridge\n- The extension injects messages into the currently active Cursor chat\n\nBut writing a VS Code extension is a significant project.\n\nLet me present the honest options to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我老实跟你说一下目前的调研结果——\n\n## `cursor agent` 为什么不能后台跑\n\n`cursor agent` 启动后会检测是不是**真正的 Windows 交互终端窗口**。如果是 `node-pty` 创建的伪终端（ConPTY），它检测到没有真实窗口句柄就直接退出，不给任何输出。\n\n我试了：\n- `node-pty` 直接 spawn → ❌ 退出码0，零输出\n- `cmd.exe /c cursor agent` → ❌ 同上\n- `cmd.exe` 交互模式里手动输入 `cursor agent` → ❌ 命令被 shell 吃掉，不启动\n- 只有 `Start-Process cmd -ArgumentList '/k cursor agent'` 开了**真实窗口**才启动成功\n\n## 能实时对话的方案\n\n### 方案 A：MCP 桥接（推荐 ⭐）\n我运行一个 MCP 服务器，你用 `cursor --add-mcp` 注册一次：\n\n```bash\ncursor --add-mpc '{\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"command\":\"node\",\"args\":[\".../mcp_server.mjs\"]}'\n```\n\n之后在 Cursor Agent 里就可以：\n```\n你: \"让 openclaw 检查支付日志区服ID的逻辑\"\nCursor: 好的，我来调用 openclaw 的工具 → 执行 → 返回结果给你\n```\n\n**优点：** 真正的实时双向对话，Cursor Agent 里直接交流\n**缺点：** 需要你在 Cursor 那边主动提起（但对话感强）\n\n### 方案 B：`--add-mcp`（实际是 --add-mcp 参数）\n这是 Cursor CLI 自带的，把 OpenClaw 注册为 Cursor 的 MCP 工具，Agent 就能直接调用我。\n\n### 方案 C：写 Cursor 扩展（最彻底但最大工程）\n写一个 VS Code 风格的 Cursor 扩展，通过 WebSocket 连到我的桥接服务，实现完全被动的消息推送。手机发消息 → 我 → 扩展 → 直接显示在 Cursor 里。\n\n---\n\n你倾向哪个？**方案 A** 我现在就能做，注册完你在 Cursor Agent 里就能跟我对话。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5462,"output":828,"cacheRead":179072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185362,"cost":{"input":0.00076468,"output":0.00023184,"cacheRead":0.005014016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0060105359999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781505209986,"responseId":"037fb527-60dd-46bc-937c-dde9d02c6aca"}}
