{"type":"message","id":"d125f1d0","parentId":"95ca900d","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:36:28.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I realize the test will try to read the MCP results from the task file. But I already wrote a task in the previous step. Let me also clear it for a clean test. Actually, let me just run the test and see.\n\nActually wrather than run another test, I've verified:\n1. MCP server initializes correctly ✅\n2. tools/list returns all 6 tools ✅\n3. tools/call execute works ✅  \n4. The task file is written correctly ✅\n5. The MCP config is in D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\mcp.json ✅\n\nLet me clean up and present the final summary to the user. Let me clean the test artifacts and write the final SKILL.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_atwuOi2ubP7DQEoH0q9M9288","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: cursor-bridge\ndescription: Bridge between OpenClaw and Cursor IDE via MCP (Model Context Protocol). Register OpenClaw as a Cursor MCP server, send instructions to Cursor agent, and get results. Trigger when user says \"cursor\", \"给cursor发消息\", \"让cursor执行\", or similar requests about sending tasks to Cursor.\n---\n\n# Cursor Agent Bridge (MCP)\n\nOpenClaw ↔ Cursor 桥接服务，通过 MCP (Model Context Protocol) 协议集成。\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### 第一步：注册 MCP 服务器（一次性）\n\n项目级配置已写入 `D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\mcp.json`，内容：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"command\": \"node\",\n      \"args\": [\".../cursor-bridge/scripts/mcp_server.mjs\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n如果 Cursor 没自动识别，重启 Cursor 即可。\n\n### 第二步：发给 Cursor 任务\n\n```bash\nnode plugin-skills/cursor-bridge/scripts/instruct_cursor.mjs \"你的指令\"\n```\n\n### 第三步：在 Cursor Agent 里执行\n\n在 Cursor 的 Agent 对话中输入：\n```\n检查一下 openclaw 有什么任务\n```\n\nCursor Agent 会调用 `get_latest_instruction` 工具获取你的指令并执行。\n\n## MCP Tools\n\n| Tool | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `execute` | 在本地执行 shell 命令 |\n| `read_file` | 读取文件内容 |\n| `write_file` | 写入/创建文件 |\n| `list_directory` | 列出目录 |\n| `get_latest_instruction` | 获取最新的待执行指令（手机飞书发来的） |\n| `search_files` | 搜索项目文件 |\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\n手机飞书 → OpenClaw → instruct_cursor.mjs → cursor_tasks.json\n                                                    ↓\nCursor Agent ← \"检查openclaw有什么任务\" ← MCP server ← \n```\n\n## Scripts\n\n| Script | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `scripts/mcp_server.mjs` | MCP 协议服务器（Cursor 连接用） |\n| `scripts/instruct_cursor.mjs` | 发送指令到 Cursor |\n\n## Config\n\n- Project MCP: `D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\mcp.json`\n- Task queue: `workspace/cursor_tasks.json`\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":173,"output":754,"cacheRead":195072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":195999,"cost":{"input":0.000024220000000000002,"output":0.00021112000000000003,"cacheRead":0.005462016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005697356}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781505381489,"responseId":"edddb15a-5736-474e-b8c1-54ea9f8ecdf9"}}
