{"type":"message","id":"d4f937e8","parentId":"cb357657","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:39:00.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cursor processes were stopped but I can't restart it due to access permission (running in a service context). The user needs to manually restart it. Let me tell them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Cursor 已关闭原进程，但重新启动需要你在桌面操作（我这里的运行权限不够直接打开 GUI 程序）。\n\n你先手动点开 Cursor 就行，`D:\\Solo\\.cursor\\mcp.json` 的配置已经写好了。重启后你在 Agent 里说：\n\n```\n检查一下 openclaw 有什么任务\n```\n\n就能看到我刚发的测试指令了 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":221,"output":118,"cacheRead":197248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":197587,"cost":{"input":0.000030940000000000005,"output":0.00003304,"cacheRead":0.005522944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005586924}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781505537402,"responseId":"3e8e1bef-8640-4e75-8ad0-9dc0e28c1b78"}}
