{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6dce4649c4b4b1c5f77cf934813\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-06-15 14:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"5bdb3c80","parentId":"bcbdf84f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:49:54.334Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"30588247","parentId":"5bdb3c80","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:49:57.031Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to add git permissions for 赵嘉浩 with Reporter role. Let me read the gitlab-permission skill to know how to do this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jgjsCMJEChN0TMvYSXMu5525","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1032,"output":92,"cacheRead":196608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":197732,"cost":{"input":0.00014448,"output":0.00002576,"cacheRead":0.005505024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005675264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781506194335,"responseId":"9bddb331-73ec-4ea2-b0ef-99f3346a1b86"}}
{"type":"message","id":"27e2fd63","parentId":"30588247","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:49:57.150Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_jgjsCMJEChN0TMvYSXMu5525","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gitlab-permission\ndescription: 管理 git.devcloud.ztgame.com 上的 GitLab 项目成员权限。支持添加/删除/修改成员，查询项目成员列表。  \n  触发词：git权限、加git权限、管理git、项目成员、gitlab权限。  \n  适用：yyzy_proj 组下的项目，叶枝君账号（Maintainer/Owner 权限）。\n---\n\n# GitLab 权限管理\n\n## 前置条件\n\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`（已保存 _gitlab_session）\n- 仅对叶枝君具有 **Maintainer(40)** 或 **Owner(50)** 权限的项目可操作\n\n## 管理的项目组（5 个核心仓库）\n\n当说「给 XX 加项目权限」时，以下 5 个仓库全部加 **Reporter(20)**（只读），除非主人明确要求更高级别：\n\n| # | 仓库 | ID | 我的权限 |\n|:-:|------|:--:|:--------:|\n| 1 | yyzy_proj/1v1/config | 5058 | Maintainer ✅ |\n| 2 | yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig | 4710 | Owner ✅ |\n| 3 | yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework | 5048 | Developer ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 4 | yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1 | 5145 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 5 | yyzy_proj/1v1/proto | 5060 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n\n> 注：仓库 3-5 需要主人先给叶枝君提升到 Maintainer 权限才能管理。\n\n## 其他可管理的项目\n\n| 项目 | ID | 权限 |\n|------|:--:|:----:|\n| yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon | 2751 | Owner |\n| didastudio/cdn_251121 | 5638 | Maintainer |\n| yezhijun1/cdn_solo | 5871 | Owner |\n\n## 权限等级\n\n| 等级 | 名称 | 值 |\n|:----:|------|:--:|\n| 10 | Guest | 访客 |\n| 20 | Reporter | 报告者 |\n| 30 | Developer | 开发者 |\n| 40 | Maintainer | 维护者 |\n| 50 | Owner | 拥有者 |\n\n## 已知用户 ID\n\n| 姓名 | 用户名 | ID |\n|------|--------|:--:|\n| 叶枝君 | @yezhijun | 983 |\n| 周以天 | @v-zhouyitian | 1003 |\n| 陈霄豪 | @chenxiaohao | 1134 |\n| 胡新雷 | @v-huxinlei | 1836 |\n\n## API 用法\n\n## 认证方式\n\nGitLab 使用公司 Keycloak SSO 登录（LDAP/CAS），需要从已登录的浏览器获取 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n\n**Cookie 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n**CSRF Token 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\n\n**写操作（POST/PUT/DELETE）** 需要 `X-CSRF-Token` 头，否则返回 401。\n登录方式：打开 headed 浏览器 → 手动 SSO 登录（先点 SSO → Keycloak 再输一次密码）→ 自动保存 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n\n```javascript\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\nconst writeHeaders = { ...headers, 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded', 'X-CSRF-Token': csrfToken };\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n```\n\n> `git_permission.mjs` 已自动处理 CSRF Token：`getHeaders()` 用于读取，`getWriteHeaders()` 用于写入。\n\n### 查询项目成员\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/all?per_page=100\n```\n\n### 批量添加到 5 个核心仓库（给项目加权限）\n```bash\nnode scripts/git_permission.mjs batch <用户名称> developer\n```\n\n### 添加成员（单一仓库）\n```bash\nPOST /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members\nBody: user_id={user_id}&access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 修改成员权限\n```bash\nPUT /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\nBody: access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 删除成员\n```bash\nDELETE /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\n```\n\n### 搜索用户\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/users?search={用户名}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781506197150}}
{"type":"message","id":"69721c4b","parentId":"27e2fd63","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:50:00.957Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to:\n1. Find 赵嘉浩's user ID by searching GitLab\n2. Add him as Reporter to the core projects\n\nBut 赵嘉浩 is not in the known users list. Let me search for him first. Also, for the \"加git权限\" task, by default it's the 5 core repos with Reporter level.\n\nLet me search for 赵嘉浩 on GitLab first, then batch add him.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6Rd4b55cG1RDizF2zvgH2808","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\"\nnode -e \"\nimport { getHeaders } from './scripts/git_permission.mjs';\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nconst res = await fetch(GITLAB + '/api/v4/users?search=' + encodeURIComponent('赵嘉浩'), {\n  headers: getHeaders()\n});\nconst users = await res.json();\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(users, null, 2));\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1196,"output":266,"cacheRead":197632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":199094,"cost":{"input":0.00016744,"output":0.00007448,"cacheRead":0.005533696,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005775616}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781506197154,"responseId":"b671ce81-ce27-44a2-bfd4-6edb74203bf1"}}
