{"type":"message","id":"1c69667d","parentId":"8938e73f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:50:36.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The GitLab cookies file doesn't exist. I need to either:\n1. Login to GitLab to generate the cookies (headed browser flow)\n2. Or use a PAT (Personal Access Token)\n\nSince I don't have the GitLab cookies, I need to tell the user. But let me first check if there's a way to get the cookies.\n\nActually, let me check if the github_cookies.json structure could work, or if there's a simpler auth method. Let me look at the script more carefully to see what it expects.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_48QWUkT6ASVU9LoTBQSe7063","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\\scripts\\git_permission.mjs","limit":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":799,"output":197,"cacheRead":201984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":202980,"cost":{"input":0.00011186,"output":0.00005516,"cacheRead":0.0056555519999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005822572}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781506233657,"responseId":"a7bd3d9b-e15d-4bc3-914b-0a1cc94a9c67"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f137ecf","parentId":"1c69667d","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:50:36.812Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_48QWUkT6ASVU9LoTBQSe7063","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * GitLab 权限管理工具\n * \n * 用法:\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs list <project_id>                          # 查看项目成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs add <project_id> <user_name> <level>       # 添加成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs update <project_id> <user_name> <level>    # 修改权限\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs remove <project_id> <user_name>            # 删除成员\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs search <keyword>                           # 搜索用户\n *   node scripts/git_permission.mjs projects                                    # 列出可管理的项目\n * \n * 权限等级: guest(10) / reporter(20) / developer(30) / maintainer(40) / owner(50)\n */\n\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..', '..', '..', 'workspace');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'gitlab_cookies.json');\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nconst LEVEL_MAP = {\n  guest: 10, '10': 10,\n  reporter: 20, '20': 20,\n  developer: 30, '30': 30,\n  maintainer: 40, '40': 40,\n  owner: 50, '50': 50,\n};\nconst LEVEL_NAMES = { 10: 'Guest', 20: 'Reporter', 30: 'Developer', 40: 'Maintainer', 50: 'Owner' };\n\nfunction getHeaders() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  return { 'Cookie': cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; '), 'Accept': 'application/json', 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' };\n}\n\nasync function searchUser(keyword) {\n  const r = await fetch(`${GITLAB}/api/v4/users?search=${encodeURIComponent(keyword)}&per_page=10`, { headers: getHeaders() });\n  const users = await r.json();\n\n[82 more lines in file. Use offset=41 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781506236811}}
{"type":"message","id":"409c3856","parentId":"8f137ecf","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:50:41.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need GitLab cookies. The user might have them saved somewhere. Let me check if I can find any cookies or if the user needs to log in. Let me tell the user about the situation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"GitLab 的 cookie 文件 (`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`) 不存在，没法直接调 API。\n\n你之前有登录过公司的 GitLab 并保存 cookie 吗？如果没的话，需要先走一遍登录流程把 cookie 存下来。\n\n不过我可以用 GitHub CLI（`gh`）来完成这件事吗？还是说这个是你们公司的自建 GitLab（`git.devcloud.ztgame.com`），只能用 session cookie 登录？\n\n需要你先在浏览器登录 GitLab，然后把 cookie 发给我，或者我帮你开 headed 浏览器你扫码登录？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":647,"output":162,"cacheRead":202880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203689,"cost":{"input":0.00009058,"output":0.000045360000000000006,"cacheRead":0.00568064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00581658}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781506236815,"responseId":"7b8ea47f-da26-4146-b3f9-2ed5dc48d0d6"}}
