{"type":"message","id":"815be7e7","parentId":"6dcabe92","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:52:27.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found 赵嘉浩: id=2068, username=@zhaojiahao. Now I need to add him as Reporter (20) to the projects.\n\nThe managed projects are:\n1. yyzy_proj/1v1/config (id=5058)\n2. yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig (id=4710)\n3. yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework (id=5048) - ❌ 无权管理\n4. yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1 (id=5145) - ❌ 无权管理\n5. yyzy_proj/1v1/proto (id=5060) - ❌ 无权管理\n\nSo only project 1 and 2 can be managed. Let me add 赵嘉浩 as Reporter to both.\n\nLet me add him to the 5 core projects per the SKILL.md default behavior, but only 1 and 2 will work.\n\nActually, I should try adding to the projects I have access to. Let me do both individually first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到赵嘉浩了（id=2068）。按默认规则给核心仓库加 Reporter 权限，不过我有权限的只有前两个："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dy0LbHjLisSSrKvtZ0HW1089","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\"\nWrite-Output \"=== 给 yyzy_proj/1v1/config 加 Reporter ===\"\nnode scripts/git_permission.mjs add 5058 赵嘉浩 reporter 2>&1\n\nWrite-Output \"`n=== 给 yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig 加 Reporter ===\"\nnode scripts/git_permission.mjs add 4710 赵嘉浩 reporter 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":70,"output":424,"cacheRead":206848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":207342,"cost":{"input":0.000009800000000000001,"output":0.00011872,"cacheRead":0.005791744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005920264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781506341960,"responseId":"3f5d32df-858f-4f3a-ba5f-831e0901db00"}}
