{"type":"message","id":"0894add1","parentId":"0672ef82","timestamp":"2026-06-15T06:53:18.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `spawn UNKNOWN` error occurs with any complex Node.js command. It seems to be triggered by certain characters or the length of the command. Let me write to a file instead.\n\nActually, a simpler approach: the 409 \"already exists\" means the user IS a member. Let me just check his current level by looking at any project's members list with a broader search.\n\nOr, better yet, since the user is already a member of all 5 projects (confirmed by 409), the question is what ACCESS LEVEL they already have. If it's already Reporter (20), we're done. If not, we need to update.\n\nBut I got NOT FOUND when checking with `/members/all` - maybe the API doesn't list them because they're from an inherited group membership and the response format is different. Let me try again with a different approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xWQgaOCpATqw2mohtsja0738","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => c.name + '=' + c.value).join('; ');\n\n// Check user 2068\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/users/2068', {\n  headers: { Cookie: cookieStr, Accept: 'application/json' }\n});\nconsole.log('User 2068:', JSON.stringify(await r.json(), null, 2));\n\n// Now check members of project 5058 \nconst r2 = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/5058/members/all?per_page=100', {\n  headers: { Cookie: cookieStr, Accept: 'application/json' }\n});\nconst members = await r2.json();\nconst zhao = members.find(m => m.id === 2068);\nif (zhao) {\n  const levels = {10:'Guest',20:'Reporter',30:'Developer',40:'Maintainer',50:'Owner'};\n  console.log(`\\n赵嘉浩 in project 5058: ${levels[zhao.access_level] || zhao.access_level} (level=${zhao.access_level})`);\n} else {\n  // Try direct members only\n  const r3 = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/5058/members?per_page=100', {\n    headers: { Cookie: cookieStr, Accept: 'application/json' }\n  });\n  const directMembers = await r3.json();\n  const zhaoDirect = directMembers.find(m => m.id === 2068);\n  if (zhaoDirect) {\n    const levels = {10:'Guest',20:'Reporter',30:'Developer',40:'Maintainer',50:'Owner'};\n    console.log(`\\n赵嘉浩 in project 5058 (direct): ${levels[zhaoDirect.access_level] || zhaoDirect.access_level}`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`\\n赵嘉浩 not found in project 5058 members, but 409 said already exists.`);\n    console.log(`Total members (all): ${members.length}`);\n    console.log(`Total members (direct): ${directMembers.length}`);\n  }\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\check_user.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":55,"output":765,"cacheRead":211328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":212148,"cost":{"input":0.0000077,"output":0.0002142,"cacheRead":0.005917184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0061390839999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781506391480,"responseId":"5fdec066-8694-45d0-b1a7-8dc4ee9dd00a"}}
