{"type":"message","id":"b7ca4b62","parentId":"722a6c0e","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:17:38.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `FindWindow($null, \"Cursor\")` also returned 0. Looking at the earlier window list, the main window title is just \"Cursor\" but maybe it needs exact match or the window has a different title format.\n\nActually, looking at the process list:\n```\n12972 Cursor     2026/6/15 14:48:08\n```\n\nThe process has MainWindowTitle = \"Cursor\". But FindWindow returns 0. Maybe the window title has spaces or special characters.\n\nLet me try EnumWindows to find all windows and search for Cursor in their titles.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ilhPZHbUcZYFwxXNETtj7710","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Use EnumWindows to find Cursor windows\n$enumSig = @'\npublic delegate bool EnumWindowsProc(IntPtr hWnd, int lParam);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\npublic static extern bool EnumWindows(EnumWindowsProc lpEnumFunc, int lParam);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\npublic static extern int GetWindowText(IntPtr hWnd, System.Text.StringBuilder text, int count);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\npublic static extern int GetWindowTextLength(IntPtr hWnd);\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\npublic static extern bool IsWindowVisible(IntPtr hWnd);\n'@\n$enumApi = Add-Type -MemberDefinition $enumSig -Name \"EnumWin\" -Namespace Win32 -PassThru\n\n$results = [System.Collections.ArrayList]::new()\n$callback = [Win32.EnumWindowsProc]{\n    param($hWnd, $lParam)\n    $len = [Win32.EnumWin]::GetWindowTextLength($hWnd)\n    if ($len -gt 0) {\n        $sb = New-Object System.Text.StringBuilder ($len + 1)\n        [Win32.EnumWin]::GetWindowText($hWnd, $sb, $len + 1)\n        $title = $sb.ToString()\n        $visible = [Win32.EnumWin]::IsWindowVisible($hWnd)\n        if ($title -match \"(?i)cursor|agent|cmd|terminal|powershell|solo|围棋|棋谱\") {\n            [void]$results.Add([PSCustomObject]@{\n                HWND = $hWnd.ToString('X')\n                Title = $title\n                Visible = $visible\n            })\n        }\n    }\n    return $true\n}\n\n[void][Win32.EnumWin]::EnumWindows($callback, 0)\n$results | Where-Object Visible | Format-Table -AutoSize","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":56,"output":599,"cacheRead":223104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":223759,"cost":{"input":0.000007840000000000001,"output":0.00016772,"cacheRead":0.006246911999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006422471999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781507850684,"responseId":"28a6aab4-8d03-4478-aaca-a1c1e94cc135"}}
{"type":"message","id":"665cef71","parentId":"b7ca4b62","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:17:42.312Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ilhPZHbUcZYFwxXNETtj7710","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找不到类型 [Win32.EnumWindowsProc]。\r\n所在位置 行:16 字符: 14\r\n+ $callback = [Win32.EnumWindowsProc]{\r\n+              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (Win32.EnumWindowsProc:TypeName) []，RuntimeException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : TypeNotFound\n\n(Command exited with code 3221226505)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":3221226505,"durationMs":4141,"aggregated":"找不到类型 [Win32.EnumWindowsProc]。\r\n所在位置 行:16 字符: 14\r\n+ $callback = [Win32.EnumWindowsProc]{\r\n+              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (Win32.EnumWindowsProc:TypeName) []，RuntimeException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : TypeNotFound\n\n(Command exited with code 3221226505)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781507862312}}
{"type":"message","id":"579d03a1","parentId":"665cef71","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:17:51.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The delegate type isn't created yet because `Add-Type` needs to compile first and the callback type definition is in the same `Add-Type` call. Let me use a different approach - find the Cursor window by class name or by enumerating with a different method.\n\nActually, you know what, let me stop trying all these complex automation approaches and give the user an honest answer about what's possible and what's the best way forward.\n\nThe reality is:\n1. `cursor agent` can be opened in a real window, but I can't reliably inject keystrokes into it from a background process\n2. Cursor's IPC protocol is undocumented and complex\n3. MCP is the supported integration mechanism, but it's pull-based (Cursor calls me)\n\nThe most practical approaches that actually work:\n1. **MCP (already set up)** - User says \"check openclaw tasks\" in Cursor\n2. **File-based watch** - User runs `/loop 30s` in Cursor once\n3. **Write a simple Cursor extension** - Most reliable, bidirectional\n\nLet me be honest with the user and recommend approach 3 (writing a Cursor extension) if they want fully automatic push.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"说实话，我试了各种方案，目前的实际情况是：\n\n**`cursor agent` 的问题：**\n- 它在后台/PTY 里**拒绝启动**，必须要有真实 Windows 窗口\n- 开了真实窗口后，从后台进程用 `SendKeys`/`PostMessage` 注入按键**权限不够**（Access denied）\n- Cursor 的 IPC 协议没公开，没法直接用 CLI 推指令\n\n**目前可用的方式对比：**\n\n| 方式 | 需要你操作吗 | 实时性 |\n|------|:----------:|:------:|\n| ✅ MCP（已配好） | 在 Agent 说句 \"检查任务\" | 手动 |\n| ✅ /loop 轮询 | 跑一次 `/loop` 就行 | ~30秒 |\n| ⏳ 写 Cursor 扩展 | **完全不需要** | **实时** |\n\n如果你想要**完全不用管，手机发消息 Cursor 自动执行**，最好的方式是方案 3——写一个 Cursor 扩展（VS Code extension），它：\n1. 在后台监听一个本地 WebSocket\n2. 我收到你的消息后推给扩展\n3. 扩展自动把指令注入到 Cursor Agent 的输入框并触发执行\n\n要不要我写这个扩展？大概需要半小时。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":121,"output":529,"cacheRead":223744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":224394,"cost":{"input":0.00001694,"output":0.00014812,"cacheRead":0.006264832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0064298919999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781507862316,"responseId":"ecae98b5-8a77-4200-8395-5a28d483b7d0"}}
