{"type":"message","id":"1517a157","parentId":"16fd93b3","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:35:12.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also update the SKILL.md and then restart Cursor to load the extension.\n\nActually wait, the instruct_cursor.mjs is an ESM file using `import WebSocket from 'ws'`. But the skill's `package.json` has `\"type\": \"commonjs\"`. ESM imports from a `.mjs` file should still work since `.mjs` is always ESM regardless of package.json.\n\nLet me verify the instruct_cursor script works by doing a quick test... but first, Cursor needs to be restarted to load the extension.\n\nLet me update the SKILL.md and then tell the user to restart Cursor.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Yveyk4BKfR7d78kAoH2x8425","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"status":"completed","step":"创建 Cursor Extension 骨架 (package.json + extension.js)"},{"status":"completed","step":"编写 WebSocket 服务器 + 自动注入 Agent 指令逻辑"},{"status":"completed","step":"安装到 Cursor 扩展目录"},{"status":"in_progress","step":"更新 SKILL.md"},{"status":"pending","step":"重启 Cursor + 验证"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":98,"output":267,"cacheRead":231040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":231405,"cost":{"input":0.00001372,"output":0.00007476000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00646912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0065576}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781508908029,"responseId":"4261b870-394f-4b3b-8d89-a1ec33107f64"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9eaaa11f","parentId":"1517a157","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:35:12.512Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Yveyk4BKfR7d78kAoH2x8425","toolName":"update_plan","content":[],"details":{"status":"updated","plan":[{"step":"创建 Cursor Extension 骨架 (package.json + extension.js)","status":"completed"},{"step":"编写 WebSocket 服务器 + 自动注入 Agent 指令逻辑","status":"completed"},{"step":"安装到 Cursor 扩展目录","status":"completed"},{"step":"更新 SKILL.md","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"重启 Cursor + 验证","status":"pending"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781508912512}}
{"type":"message","id":"07ed00d5","parentId":"9eaaa11f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:35:17.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ET_UU7TZRfRvuHdfhO2EBLx5709","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: cursor-bridge\ndescription: Bridge between OpenClaw and Cursor IDE via MCP (Model Context Protocol) and WebSocket extension. Register OpenClaw as a Cursor MCP server, send instructions to Cursor agent via WebSocket extension, and get results. Trigger when user says \"cursor\", \"给cursor发消息\", \"让cursor执行\", or similar requests about sending tasks to Cursor.\n---\n\n# Cursor Agent Bridge\n\nOpenClaw ↔ Cursor 桥接，支持两种方式：\n\n## 方式一：Cursor 扩展（推荐 ⭐）\n\n一键推送，不需要任何手动操作。\n\n### 安装\n\n扩展已安装到 `~/.cursor/extensions/cursor-bridge/`，**重启 Cursor** 后自动激活。\n\n扩展会：\n- 在 `ws://127.0.0.1:18792` 启动 WebSocket 服务\n- 收到指令后自动打开 Cursor Agent 面板并提交执行\n\n### 使用\n\n```bash\nnode plugin-skills/cursor-bridge/scripts/instruct_cursor.mjs \"你的指令\"\n```\n\n### 工作方式\n\n```\n手机飞书 → OpenClaw → WebSocket → Cursor 扩展 → 自动填入 Agent → 执行\n```\n\n## 方式二：MCP（备选）\n\n```bash\n# 在 Cursor Agent 中说：\n检查一下 openclaw 有什么任务\n```\n\n## Scripts\n\n| Script | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `scripts/instruct_cursor.mjs` | 通过 WebSocket 发送指令到 Cursor（首选） |\n| `scripts/mcp_server.mjs` | MCP 协议服务器（备选） |\n| `scripts/bridge_server.mjs` | PTY 桥接服务（已废弃） |\n\n## Extension\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `extension/package.json` | Cursor 扩展清单 |\n| `extension/extension.js` | WebSocket 服务 + Agent 注入逻辑 |\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":124,"output":500,"cacheRead":231296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":231920,"cost":{"input":0.00001736,"output":0.00014000000000000001,"cacheRead":0.006476288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006633648}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781508912516,"responseId":"6ccb6a37-df54-49bc-8fa9-b8c1