{"type":"message","id":"12ca0c62","parentId":"b0008fe2","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:35:25.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cursor 扩展已写好并安装 ✅\n\n**扩展信息：**\n- 位置：`~/.cursor/extensions/cursor-bridge/`\n- 端口：`ws://127.0.0.1:18792`\n- 行为：收到指令 → 自动打开 Agent 面板 → 填入内容 → 提交执行\n\n**需要你操作一步：**\n\n1. **重启 Cursor**（我刚才关掉了，你手动点开）\n2. 在 Cursor 里打开 **命令面板** (`Ctrl+Shift+P`)，输入 `Developer: Toggle Developer Tools`\n3. 看 **Console** 面板有没有输出 `[bridge] ✅ Ready on ws://127.0.0.1:18792`，确认扩展已启动\n\n确认扩展运行后告诉我就行，我发个测试指令过去试试能不能自动执行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":74,"output":180,"cacheRead":232064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":232318,"cost":{"input":0.00001036,"output":0.000050400000000000005,"cacheRead":0.006497792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006558552}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781508920636,"responseId":"8bd2b3d6-bc84-4bc7-a6e3-79b5e2fd1ff2"}}
