{"type":"message","id":"82dd53b7","parentId":"6a89efe5","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:37:32.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The extension didn't show any logs in the console. This could be because:\n\n1. Cursor might not have loaded the extension at all (it's not in a standard VS Code extensions path for Cursor)\n2. The extension might have failed to activate\n3. There might be a different extensions path for Cursor\n\nLet me check where Cursor loads extensions from. In VS Code, extensions are loaded from:\n- `~/.vscode/extensions/`\n- `~/.cursor/extensions/` (for Cursor-specific)\n\nBut Cursor might use a different path. Let me check.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NNRK12nCX65OAMDSJYqd9113","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 Cursor 加载扩展的路径\n# Cursor 基于 VS Code，扩展目录可能在多个位置\n\n# 1. 检查 Cursor 的扩展目录\nWrite-Output \"=== Cursor extensions dir ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\" -Name -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\nWrite-Output \"`n=== VS Code extensions dir ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.vscode\\extensions\" -Name -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# 2. 检查 Cursor 的扩展列表\nWrite-Output \"`n=== Cursor installed extensions ===\"\ncursor --list-extensions 2>&1 | Select-Object -First 20\n\n# 3. 查看 Cursor 的 extensions.json\nWrite-Output \"`n=== Cursor extensions config ===\"\nGet-Content \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\\extensions.json\" -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object -First 30","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":230966,"output":406,"cacheRead":1408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":232780,"cost":{"input":0.03233524,"output":0.00011368000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000039424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032488344}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509044866,"responseId":"1bf60c6f-afaf-4cc0-b0fe-b476e1d14e84"}}
