{"type":"message","id":"c45ce1ee","parentId":"4f6b968f","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:38:03.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Copy the updated extension to the Cursor extensions directory\n2. Update the instruct_cursor.mjs to use HTTP instead of WebSocket\n3. Restart Cursor\n4. Test\n\nLet me also fix the `publisher` field in package.json - it needs to match what Cursor sees.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_BxUVfD2CaR82T2YE8eBN1468","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 复制更新后的扩展\nCopy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\extension\\extension.js\" \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\\cursor-bridge\\extension.js\" -Force\nCopy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\extension\\package.json\" \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\\cursor-bridge\\package.json\" -Force\n\n# 更新 extensions.json 添加 metadata 让 Cursor 正确加载\n$extJsonPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\\extensions.json\"\n$extJson = Get-Content $extJsonPath -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json\n\n# 更新 cursor-bridge 扩展的 metadata\nforeach ($ext in $extJson) {\n    if ($ext.identifier.id -eq \"openclaw.cursor-bridge\") {\n        $ext.metadata = @{\n            isApplicationScoped = $false\n            isMachineScoped = $false\n            isBuiltin = $false\n            installedTimestamp = [long](Get-Date -UFormat %s) * 1000\n            pinned = $false\n            source = \"user\"\n            publisherId = \"openclaw\"\n            publisherDisplayName = \"OpenClaw\"\n            targetPlatform = \"undefined\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n$extJson | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10 | Out-File -FilePath $extJsonPath -Encoding utf8 -Force\nWrite-Output \"Updated extensions.json\"\n\n# 更新 instruct_cursor.mjs 使用 HTTP 替代 WebSocket\nWrite-Output \"`nReady for restart and test\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":172,"output":496,"cacheRead":236160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":236828,"cost":{"input":0.000024080000000000003,"output":0.00013888,"cacheRead":0.00661248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00677544}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509078678,"responseId":"ef723ca7-e7f7-4a9e-b994-e598d671dc02"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7c8b543","parentId":"c45ce1ee","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:38:04.235Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_BxUVfD2CaR82T2YE8eBN1468","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"设置“metadata”时发生异常:“在此对象上找不到属性“metadata”。请确认该属性存在并且可设置。”\r\n所在位置 行:12 字符: 9\r\n+         $ext.metadata = @{\r\n+         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], SetValueInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : ExceptionWhenSetting\r\n \r\nUpdated extensions.json\r\n\nReady for restart and test"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":270,"aggregated":"设置“metadata”时发生异常:“在此对象上找不到属性“metadata”。请确认该属性存在并且可设置。”\r\n所在位置 行:12 字符: 9\r\n+         $ext.metadata = @{\r\n+         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [], SetValueInvocationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : ExceptionWhenSetting\r\n \r\nUpdated extensions.json\r\n\nReady for restart and test","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781509084235}}
{"type":"message","id":"c63b7b15","parentId":"d7c8b543","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:38:10.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The JSON update failed due to PowerShell's object handling. Let me just write it directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2WreLBaH8vwOw2QGJ4tT8793","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接写 extensions.json\n$content = @'\n[\n  {\n    \"identifier\": { \"id\": \"anysphere.remote-ssh\", \"uuid\": \"73a45d83-83c7-4b22-bebf-c9130b0ab3f3\" },\n    \"version\": \"1.1.3\",\n    \"location\": { \"$mid\": 1, \"path\": \"/c:/Users/yyzypublic/.cursor/extensions/anysphere.remote-ssh-1.1.3\", \"scheme\": \"file\" },\n    \"relativeLocation\": \"anysphere.remote-ssh-1.1.3\",\n    \"metadata\": {\n      \"isApplicationScoped\": true, \"isMachineScoped\": false, \"isBuiltin\": false,\n      \"installedTimestamp\": 1781409295899, \"pinned\": false, \"source\": \"gallery\",\n      \"id\": \"73a45d83-83c7-4b22-bebf-c9130b0ab3f3\",\n      \"publisherId\": \"c16ea17f-2629-4893-9064-35c0fd9add4c\",\n      \"publisherDisplayName\": \"Anysphere\", \"targetPlatform\": \"undefined\",\n      \"updated\": true, \"private\": false, \"isPreReleaseVersion\": false, \"hasPreReleaseVersion\": false, \"preRelease\": false\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"identifier\": { \"id\": \"openclaw.cursor-bridge\" },\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"location\": { \"$mid\": 1, \"fsPath\": \"c:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.cursor\\\\extensions\\\\cursor-bridge\", \"_sep\": 1, \"external\": \"file:///c%3A/Users/yyzypublic/.cursor/extensions/cursor-bridge\", \"path\": \"/c:/Users/yyzypublic/.cursor/extensions/cursor-bridge\", \"scheme\": \"file\" },\n    \"relativeLocation\": \"cursor-bridge\",\n    \"metadata\": {\n      \"isApplicationScoped\": false, \"isMachineScoped\": false, \"isBuiltin\": false,\n      \"installedTimestamp\": 1781490000000, \"pinned\": false, \"source\": \"user\",\n      \"publisherId\": \"openclaw\", \"publisherDisplayName\": \"OpenClaw\",\n      \"targetPlatform\": \"undefined\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n'@\n$content | Out-File -FilePath \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.cursor\\extensions\\extensions.json\" -Encoding utf8 -Force\nWrite-Output \"extensions.json updated\"\n\n# 更新 instruct_cursor.mjs 使用 HTTP 替代 WebSocket\nWrite-Output \"`nNow restart Cursor to load the updated extension\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":144,"output":699,"cacheRead":236800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":237643,"cost":{"input":0.00002016,"output":0.00019572,"cacheRead":0.0066304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00684628}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509084239,"responseId":"3a6c1f87-79a6-4b8a-9883-8c20121c15be"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b56ad3a4","parentId":"c63b7b15","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:38:10.412Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_2WreLBaH8vwOw2QGJ4tT8793","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"extensions.json updated\r\n\nNow restart Cursor to load the updated extension"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":185,"aggregated":"extensions.json updated\r\n\nNow restart Cursor to load the updated extension","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781509090412}}
{"type":"message","id":"c548501c","parentId":"b56ad3a4","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:38:17.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the instruct_cursor.mjs script to use HTTP instead of WebSocket.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_YKhwSznmmu3EcrsdTmtW8260","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n/**\n * Send instruction to Cursor via HTTP bridge extension.\n *\n * The Cursor Bridge extension runs an HTTP server on http://127.0.0.1:18792.\n * This script POSTs the instruction to /execute.\n *\n * Usage:\n *   node instruct_cursor.mjs \"your instruction\"\n *   curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18792/execute -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"instruction\":\"hi\"}'\n */\n\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport http from 'http';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '../../../workspace');\nconst TASKS_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'cursor_tasks.json');\n\nconst PORT = 18792;\nconst instruction = process.argv.slice(2).join(' ').trim();\n\nif (!instruction) {\n  console.error('Usage: node instruct_cursor.mjs <instruction>');\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\n// Also save as fallback task file (for MCP path)\nconst task = {\n  taskId: Date.now().toString(36),\n  timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n  timeLabel: new Date().toLocaleString('zh-CN', { timeZone: 'Asia/Shanghai' }),\n  from: '叶枝君 (手机飞书)',\n  instruction,\n  status: 'pending',\n};\nfs.writeFileSync(TASKS_FILE, JSON.stringify(task, null, 2), 'utf8');\n\nconsole.log(`[bridge] Sending instruction to Cursor extension (http://127.0.0.1:${PORT}/execute)...`);\nconsole.log(`[bridge] Instruction: ${instruction.substring(0, 120)}...`);\n\nconst postData = JSON.stringify({ instruction });\n\nconst req = http.request({\n  hostname: '127.0.0.1',\n  port: PORT,\n  path: '/execute',\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n    'Content-Length': Buffer.byteLength(postData),\n  },\n  timeout: 10000,\n}, (res) => {\n  let body = '';\n  res.on('data', chunk => body += chunk);\n  res.on('end', () => {\n    try {\n      const result = JSON.parse(body);\n      if (result.success) {\n        console.log(`[bridge] ✅ ${result.message}`);\n        // Update task status\n        try {\n          const t = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(TASKS_FILE, 'utf8'));\n          t.status = 'completed';\n          t.deliveredAt = new Date().toISOString();\n          t.deliveryMethod = 'http';\n          fs.writeFileSync(TASKS_FILE, JSON.stringify(t, null, 2), 'utf8');\n        } catch (_) {}\n        process.exit(0);\n      } else {\n        console.log(`[bridge] ⚠️  ${result.message}`);\n        process.exit(1);\n      }\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.log(`[bridge] Response: ${body.substring(0, 300)}`);\n      process.exit(2);\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nreq.on('error', (err) => {\n  if (err.code === 'ECONNREFUSED') {\n    console.log(`[bridge] ❌ Cannot connect to Cursor extension at port ${PORT}`);\n    console.log(`[bridge]    Is Cursor running with the bridge extension?`);\n    console.log(`[bridge]    Restart Cursor and try again.`);\n    console.log(``);\n    console.log(`[bridge]    ⏩ Fallback: Instruction saved to cursor_tasks.json`);\n    console.log(`[bridge]    In Cursor Agent, type: \"检查一下 openclaw 有什么任务\"`);\n  } else {\n    console.log(`[bridge] ❌ Connection error: ${err.message}`);\n  }\n  process.exit(2);\n});\n\nreq.write(postData);\nreq.end();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\cursor-bridge\\scripts\\instruct_cursor.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":102,"output":984,"cacheRead":237568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":238654,"cost":{"input":0.00001428,"output":0.00027552,"cacheRead":0.006651904,"cacheWr