{"type":"message","id":"13f1e1bd","parentId":"4a710057","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:42:49.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see important info in the logs:\n\n1. `sharedprocess.log:11:2026-06-15 15:34:54.971 [info] Added extensions to default profile from external source [\"openclaw.cursor-bridge\"]` - The extension WAS detected!\n\n2. The extension host process (PID 18712) started at 14:48:15 and stopped at 15:35:39.\n\n3. But the extension host exited at 15:35:38 (all PIDs exited with code 0).\n\n4. The extension might have been activated, but the extension host was killed when Cursor's window changed.\n\nWait, I see the logs are from `20260615T144811` which was 14:48 - that's when Cursor was last started (not restarted after I updated the extension). The `sharedprocess.log` mentions \"Added extensions to default profile from external source\" which is good.\n\nLet me check the CURRENT Cursor session's logs by looking at the time. The current time is ~15:42, and the main log from `20260615T144811` was last updated at 15:35. This means Cursor hasn't been restarted recently.\n\nActually, wait - I need to check if the latest main.log has updated information. Let me check when Cursor was last started.\n\nActually, looking at the process list, `Cursor Agents` is the main window title and Cursor is running. But the log `20260615T144811` is from 14:48. If Cursor was restarted, there would be a new log folder.\n\nLet me check if there's a more recent log folder.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0imOkKR6e9sTGV2EKwnz8258","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查最新的日志\n$latestLogs = Get-ChildItem \"$env:APPDATA\\Cursor\\logs\" -Directory | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 3\n$latestLogs | ForEach-Object { Write-Output \"$($_.Name) - $($_.LastWriteTime)\" }\n\n# 检查最新的 main.log 中 extension 相关\n$latestMain = $latestLogs[0].FullName + \"\\main.log\"\nif (Test-Path $latestMain) {\n    Write-Output \"`n=== Latest main.log extension entries ===\"\n    Select-String -Path $latestMain -Pattern \"extension|bridge|cursor-bridge\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object -First 15\n}\n\n# 检查 sharedprocess.log\n$latestShared = $latestLogs[0].FullName + \"\\sharedprocess.log\"\nif (Test-Path $latestShared) {\n    Write-Output \"`n=== Latest sharedprocess.log ===\"\n    Select-String -Path $latestShared -Pattern \"extension|bridge|cursor-bridge\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object -First 15\n}\n\n# 看看 extension host 的启动情况\nWrite-Output \"`n=== Extension host system info ===\"\nGet-Process -Name \"Cursor\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime, @{N='HasMainWin';E={[bool]$_.MainWindowHandle}} | Sort-Object StartTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 5","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3565,"output":744,"cacheRead":240768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":245077,"cost":{"input":0.0004991,"output":0.00020832,"cacheRead":0.006741504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007448924}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509358957,"responseId":"6a78928d-b4c4-45b9-827d-39b39ba007a1"}}
