{"type":"message","id":"24bedc33","parentId":"e2813c8a","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:43:21.773Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ny57NJk6BXeAb7TF2L4c1115","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> 2026-06-15 15:41:45.425 [info] Getting extensions control\r\n\n=== Check if extension was added to profile ===\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:45.425 [info] Getting extensions control\r\n\n=== Check main.log for ALL content ===\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.813 [info] [RendererPing] enabled (intervalMs=5000, blockThresholdMs=15000, stacks=true)\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.824 [info] updateURL https://api2.cursor.sh/updates/api/update/win32-x64-user/cursor/3.7.36/e3c699dd1b442fbc74853e03db7e9ffe8c415f40145b1e4e968cebdf5c456684/stable\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.824 [info] update#setState idle\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:44.604 [info] [LocalAgentStorage] Scanned 1 recent databases (skipped 1 old), found 8 agent headers, deduped to 8\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:56.481 [info] [CursorProclistService] Config enabled feature (subsample every 10s)\r\n2026-06-15 15:42:11.279 [info] update#setState checking for updates\r\n2026-06-15 15:42:11.525 [info] update#setState idle"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":232,"aggregated":"> 2026-06-15 15:41:45.425 [info] Getting extensions control\r\n\n=== Check if extension was added to profile ===\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:45.425 [info] Getting extensions control\r\n\n=== Check main.log for ALL content ===\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.813 [info] [RendererPing] enabled (intervalMs=5000, blockThresholdMs=15000, stacks=true)\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.824 [info] updateURL https://api2.cursor.sh/updates/api/update/win32-x64-user/cursor/3.7.36/e3c699dd1b442fbc74853e03db7e9ffe8c415f40145b1e4e968cebdf5c456684/stable\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:41.824 [info] update#setState idle\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:44.604 [info] [LocalAgentStorage] Scanned 1 recent databases (skipped 1 old), found 8 agent headers, deduped to 8\r\n2026-06-15 15:41:56.481 [info] [CursorProclistServi