{"type":"message","id":"45697dc7","parentId":"24bedc33","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:43:28.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The `main.log` is very sparse - it doesn't mention extensions being loaded at all. In the previous session, the log showed \"Extension host with pid ... exited with code: 0\" and \"Added extensions to default profile from external source\". But in this new session, there's no mention of extensions being loaded.\n\nThis suggests the shared process might not be loading extensions. The log only shows \"Getting extensions control\" but no \"Added extensions\".\n\nLet me check if there's an `extensionHost` log or more detailed logging. \n\nActually, let me try a different approach. Instead of debugging why the extension doesn't load, let me:\n1. Check if the extension is in Cursor's disabled list\n2. Try activating it manually\n3. Or use a different installation method\n\nLet me check Cursor's settings for disabled extensions.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wSqffYoHwsKnwCcFi8wL5416","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if extension is disabled\n$settingsPath = \"$env:APPDATA\\Cursor\\User\\settings.json\"\nif (Test-Path $settingsPath) {\n    $settings = Get-Content $settingsPath -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json\n    Write-Output \"Settings keys with 'extension' or 'disabled':\"\n    $settings.PSObject.Properties | Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"extension|disabled\" } | Select-Object Name, Value\n}\n\n# Check Cursor's product.json for extension configuration\n$productPath = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\cursor\\resources\\app\\product.json\"\nif (Test-Path $productPath) {\n    $product = Get-Content $productPath -Raw | ConvertFrom-Json\n    Write-Output \"`nProduct.json extension related keys:\"\n    $product.PSObject.Properties | Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"extension\" } | ForEach-Object { \n        Write-Output \"  $($_.Name): $($_.Value | ConvertTo-Json -Compress -Depth 2)\"\n    }\n}","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":411,"output":482,"cacheRead":249728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":250621,"cost":{"input":0.00005754,"output":0.00013496000000000002,"cacheRead":0.006992384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007184884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509401777,"responseId":"46fb9d4d-cf87-4dc0-8f6d-f1f15279f43e"}}
