{"type":"message","id":"1a5dee91","parentId":"d024f45b","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:44:22.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I've closed Cursor and cleared the logs. The new extension version:\n\n1. Uses only pure VS Code API (no `http`, no `net`)\n2. Polls `cursor_tasks.json` every 5 seconds for new pending tasks\n3. When a task is found, it:\n   - Opens the Cursor agent panel\n   - Sets the clipboard\n   - Tries to paste and send\n4. Writes debug logs to `cursor_bridge_debug.log`\n\nI need the user to restart Cursor and check the debug log. Let me tell them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"简化了扩展，去掉了 `http` 模块，改用文件轮询方式（每 5 秒检查一次 `cursor_tasks.json`）。\n\n**你操作：**\n1. **重启 Cursor**（桌面点开）\n2. 等几秒后，检查这个文件有没有日志：\n   ```\n   %USERPROFILE%\\.openclaw\\workspace\\cursor_bridge_debug.log\n   ```\n\n如果有日志说 \"=== ACTIVATED ===\"，说明扩展加载成功。然后告诉我，我发条测试指令过去看看能不能自动执行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":109,"output":239,"cacheRead":266624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":266972,"cost":{"input":0.00001526,"output":0.00006692,"cacheRead":0.007465472,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007547652}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781509458195,"responseId":"6d826dc3-ef73-44e3-9276-bacbdd972ddd"}}
