{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6dce931bd8b4b1d93bea9044463\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-06-15 15:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"102f7077","parentId":"bbdf2992","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:46:42.211Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"af16aaa1","parentId":"102f7077","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:46:48.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"发消息\" - send a message. They want me to send a test instruction to Cursor. Let me check if the extension bridge is working by writing a task to the cursor_tasks.json file. The extension polls this file every 5 seconds.\n\nLet me write a test instruction to cursor_tasks.json.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aEjRSPayYwtpgOjXPwiE3912","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 debug 日志\n$log = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\cursor_bridge_debug.log\"\nif (Test-Path $log) {\n    Write-Output \"=== Debug Log ===\"\n    Get-Content $log\n} else {\n    Write-Output \"Debug log not found - extension may not have loaded\"\n}\n\n# 检查端口（旧版 HTTP 扩展可能还在）\nnetstat -ano 2>$null | Select-String \"18792\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":27804,"output":233,"cacheRead":232832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":260869,"cost":{"input":0.00389256,"output":0.00006524,"cacheRead":0.006519296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010477096}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781509602212,"responseId":"199d6f55-4935-41ff-aa43-10984e50864f"}}
