{"type":"message","id":"8c403cc3","parentId":"7ce981f4","timestamp":"2026-06-15T07:46:55.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The extension still hasn't loaded. The debug log file doesn't exist, which means the extension was never activated.\n\nLet me try a different approach. Instead of trying to write a VS Code extension, let me check if there's a simpler way. Maybe I should check the `sharedprocess.log` to see why the extension isn't being loaded.\n\nActually, let me check what happened with the latest Cursor restart.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vjPHZiMP9J96iItS7qx24000","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查最新的日志\n$logDir = Get-ChildItem \"$env:APPDATA\\Cursor\\logs\" -Directory | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 1\nWrite-Output \"Latest log dir: $($logDir.Name) ($($logDir.LastWriteTime))\"\n\n# 检查 renderer.log\nif (Test-Path \"$($logDir.FullName)\\window1_wb0\\renderer.log\") {\n    Write-Output \"`n=== Renderer log (bridge/extension relevant) ===\"\n    Select-String -Path \"$($logDir.FullName)\\window1_wb0\\renderer.log\" -Pattern \"bridge|extension|activated\" | Select-Object -First 15\n}\n\n# 检查 sharedprocess.log\nif (Test-Path \"$($logDir.FullName)\\sharedprocess.log\") {\n    Write-Output \"`n=== Shared process log ===\"\n    Get-Content \"$($logDir.FullName)\\sharedprocess.log\"\n}\n\n# 检查 main.log \nif (Test-Path \"$($logDir.FullName)\\main.log\") {\n    Write-Output \"`n=== Main log ===\"\n    Get-Content \"$($logDir.FullName)\\main.log\" | Select-Object -Last 10\n}\n\n# Cursor 运行的进程数\nWrite-Output \"`n=== Cursor processes ===\"\nGet-Process -Name \"Cursor\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Measure-Object | Select-Object Count","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":27,"output":467,"cacheRead":260864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":261358,"cost":{"input":0.000003780000